comments: ["It is a total waste of time and money. It does not matter if you have premium, you won't be receiving any matches at all (I had subscribed to the premium, still the same). It's like a window shopping app where you just keep scrolling and scrolling until you're satisfied without hoping to get anything. For once I thought this app could be genuine and I purchased the premium, but no, if all I had to do was left and right swipe people, I might have as well stayed on Tinder for free.", 'The UI is quite user friendly. But few things which can be improved on. 1. Message notification doesn\'t pop up a lot of times 2. Call notification doesn\'t pop up ever, plus call drops multiple times 3. Filter option doesn\'t work properly, for example if I choose age range 33-36, I still see people of age 23 4. Algo for common interest can be improved specially for best bees feed, I get best bees who want "Something Casual" while my preference is "Relationship"', 'I can not escape the feeling of a jacked up algorithm. One that puts people on the bottom despite their subscription in some sort of "lead with a carrot" business model. That or no one\'s on this app, and the app does not seem to want to take people who have not been on the app in months in the algorithm. Furthermore, there seems to be no quick, obvious, and easy way to end your subscription.', "I used the app for about one year and had a few decent dates out of it. However, as soon as my paid membership expired, literally overnight, I went from having zero people interested in me to 47, of course being prompted to go back to the paid version. Didn't change location or filters during that time, so obviously, they are manipulating the truth and the end user.", 'For an app that requires access to your location, you\'d think they\'d give you an accurate mileage estimate for people near you, but nope they can\'t be bothered to do that. Just saw someone who lives in the next state over from me and, according to Bumble, they\'re 85 miles away from me. However, when I enter the city on Google maps, it gives me a much more accurate mileage: 156 miles. That\'s a 71 mile difference, nearly double Bumble\'s "estimate."', 'The worst of all dating apps. Like Tinder, gives you options from ridiculous distances, especially if youre in rural areas. Most people are visitors from very far. The worst part is once youve swiped left on a potential match they are removed from your likes and you probably will never see them again."you\'ve missed a potential match" forever. Also they put the location at the bottom so you have to scroll the whole profile just to see the distance factor. Overall a very bad experience', "This app is ok but needs work. I canceled my premium. One of the big thing that must be added is letting me know when the last time a person logged on. That way I'm not wasting time on someone who hasn't logged on in a month. That's a waste of a swipe especially a super swipe. Also need to separate straight people from gay. As I have swiped on the wrong person and they get all offended. If these things were fixed I would keep logging in.", "I have emailed support multiple times about transferring my premium subscription from a previously deleted account to my new account and there has been absolutely no response from anyone in support. Unlike other dating apps that allow you to re-instate previously purchased subscriptions without having to email support (that doesn't respond to you anyway), Bumble just really need to sort its issues out.", "Terrible app! you have to pay for basic Things like just to see who liked you you can only see the people that complimented your profile and that's limited, You have to pay for everything like super swipes & to go back if you made a mistake. They took down one of my photos for going against community guide lines but it's a picture of me in a long dress no nudity nothing inappropriate. & whatever preferences youre allowed to choose (age and distance) doesn't narrow down the field", "Still an awful app, I've tried it multiple times and men never see their related matches. We get search results from 97 miles away from people who don't match our criteria. And you can tell even from the blurry images that you never see the people who actually do swipe on you. It's entirely designed to keep you swiping without any actual results. Don't waste your time", 'Waste of time and money, the location of people is totally hit and miss, when you do "match" with someone it is debatable if they are actually real or generated by the app to keep you interested. For an app that is meant to compliment your social circle/find people with similar interests and so on, no one actually talks. Might just stick with the old-fashioned way!', "All the other dating apps I get plenty of matches, but bumble is awful at what it's supposed to do. No matches, and because of the time limit to message you often miss the matches you do get. Pointless app and a waste of time. Edited, after the reply I received more likes than before after I left a review, strange, then they started to get less and Ive just realised the compliment feature has been removed. I think the free compliments were the only thing that made bumble worth using.", "Because you can't filter results by important categories like religion without paying, the app is essentially useless. You are forced to weed through thousands of profiles that aren't close to your value specifications. The profiles layout is also a mess, listing interests in a buckshot-style jumble where things like children, religion, age, location, etc are thrown into the mix randomly and you have to look around more to find it (those should be at the top of the list).", "I think it's more likely to get struck by lightning and win the lottery at the same time than get a match. It's way too easy to accidentally swipe left, and those swiped on can't come back, and the highlights cost 8 bucks each. Like, who even? Fix your app.", "What's the use of having the dating interface if you can't even contact/connect to a prospect without having to pay a bloody fee? And even then, even if you do want to spend on it, the chances of getting catfished is unbelievably high. The aspect of this side of the app is completely useless. I will give it props if you're using it for business networking purposes and works well if that is your ONLY objective. The dating interface is bonkers.", "it's very picky and decisive wanting you to spend money just like any other app. they shouldn't just give the option free to connect with anyone but they should make a lot easier if you want to say hello or block or do what you would like explicit or not. there's filters for everything. just make it all around app that everybody can use. it's 2023 and this is the longest run on sentence I've ever done. but we all know what we're looking for in the beginning and in the end and who may b in middle", 'It\'s just as bad if not worse than Tinder surprisingly. Customer service is 0/10. I can\'t get a hold of any humans to discuss my problems, I\'ve sent at least 10 emails. I get photos randomly taken down because they "violate" community standards according to the algorithm. I\'ve purchased the lifetime membership twice and, like anyone, deleted and reinstalled the app many times, but now I dont have the lifetime membership, and they won\'t fix it. Summary: All dating apps suck.', 'Bait and switched into "subscription". If I wanted to continue after the 1 month trial I agreed to paid for, I would have chosen a less expensive package. I cancelled the subscription and contacted support 20 minutes after charged, I had to open a PayPal case. 2 weeks later Bumble hasnt responsed. Bait and switch auto-subscriptions are theft. Ive lost $60 to this "free" app and have zero dates to show for it, just "content sellers" posting their Instagram and onlyfans.', 'Totally wast of time & Money, I have not received positive responses from the opposite gender. The 30-minute spotlight feature, promising up to 10x matches, did not help. People seem less active, making it challenging to find potential matches. Considering trying other apps, Bumble has not been useful recently. I do not recommend it based on my recent experiences.', "Bumble is useless without a premium subscription. All filters except age & distance are now locked behind a paywall, so rooting through all the bad matches to find someone is a chore. You only get 24 hours to respond to a match, otherwise you have to pay to rematch. And if you accidentally swipe left on someone you do want to match with, you have to pay to undo it. If the woman matches but doesn't start chatting within 24 hours, (Something that happens A LOT) the match disappears completely.", "Not sure how I feel about it. So far I like how the verification process goes and the app runs smooth but been on it for 2 weeks with premium and not worth it. You don't really get as much people due to the fact that the premium is expensive and also the notification when you do get someone doesn't really appear on either the app notification or email. Also anyone you've liked you can't tell if they even seen the like. Definitely needs more work for the cost.", "I like this app, in my opinion it' s very nice but it's just ridiculously expensive. probably the most expensive app I've tried. so I subscribed in different app although I still use the free features on Bumble. Some things could be better. don't like the fact that only match girls can do first move, think that's silly. I've been on a date with a girl and she complained that men never say anything, then I said we can't, first move has to be from girl.", "When you pay to upgrade and it run out. I have found that when you get likes the system doesn't match you with them. I wants you to upgrade. They then timed out and their gone. Don't pay for the upgrade or you'll just have to delete your account like I did. It should be above all, about finding a connection.", 'Having a limit on likes per day isn\'t a bad idea, but this app\'s limit is almost cartoonish. I can\'t spend more than a few minutes per 24 hours swiping without being told I need to pay 3 WHOLE DOLLARS to keep going. It\'s asinine. On top of that, almost everything else is locked behind paywalls. Though I do like that you can list your pronouns without having to first pick "man or woman." But that\'s just basic decency, not a feature', "I've been on Bumble for a few weeks now. Ended up paying for the boost, matched with someone who, for their prompt, asked me to verify my photo. Prior to this I had tried probably 20 times to verify, and was never able to. Yes I tried photos with just myself. Mimicking the pose, hand gestures, and even location exactly, but couldn't verify. Now I'm stuck on the verification screen, I'm being ignored by the support team. 0/5", "To the pros: fairly clean & simple UI, tho a bit outdated. Cons: gps based search, meaning swiping endlessly tons of people in proximity, including tourists & people in the airport and there's no way to filter out. And you have to scroll all way down to find out person is living somewhere else or doesn't disclose. So looks like tinder at this point and more oriented towards finding one night stand nearby. Exhausting & very disappointing experience for me and after a long time trying it, I'm out", "So there is a subscription model for 21 dollars a month, but this subscription does not come with the ability to see who likes you. For that, you'd need ANOTHER subscription 13 dollars more expensive than the regular subscription. To unlock seeing who likes you, you have to pay 35 bucks a month. That's gotta be an accident, right? Why would this feature not be in the regular subscription?", "Don't buy the spot lights!!!! The app will self activate them and email support stopped trying to help! I tried just not being on for a couple days till subscription weekly one was added when I did log on it has already used it and times out! Yes I emailed them and they tried a couple time but stopped helping. Lost 5 so far. And they are not doing anything to help. Very disappointed in you guys. I'm done I've cancelled the subscription and not trying to get your help when you just blow it off.", "It's...ehhh. My issues are the inability to filter out poly/ENM profiles looking for unicorns, continuing to get likes from men when I am a lesbian, the constant message ads and empty notifications, and the high cost of premium. Been using it for a few months now, met one potential person but I'm demoralized. I won't renew my subscription.", 'I tried several times to get my picture verified, including taking a picture, posting it, and then without moving, taking the same picture in the verify area. They still said I could not be verified. I contacted customer service about it, and my app got stuck on the verify photo page and would not leave that page. I then contacted customer service two more times about it and still stuck. It would be nice to at least be able to try the app out.', "Well developed but core functionality is behind a paywall, and there's no incentive to pay for an app that feels dead. Honestly it looks great but actually seeing who has matched you is behind a pricy paywall, so it's a dice roll as to whether two people see each other, and this makes the limited ability to like people (an otherwise good feature) greatly lower the ceiling on chances of matching. People have moved onto other apps.", 'The app needs work on how it recognizes and interacts with phone media. It\'s difficult to get it to recognize videos & it has double standards when it comes to photos and videos. The app allows the most pixelated pictures you\'ll ever see; however, it won\'t let me upload perfectly fine videos due to "low quality" (they\'re not), wrong dimensions (huh?), or not being shot on my phone (really?). So far, it\'s not very user-friendly.', "Swear this app is a con. I have 9 so say 'matches waiting for me'. I just used a boost and spent the full 30 minutes swiping to see if I would get anywhere with any of them (get rid of or properly match with them) and I didn't come across a single one of these people. It is so blatantly a scam just to make people feel like they have no option but to pay to see more etc etc...", "The customer service for Bumble is absolutely terrible!! I have contacted them over 10 times in a two week span and Bumble has not replied to ANY of my inquiries. My account is stuck on photo verification and I cannot access any othet part of my account. I am currently paying for the Premium option as well. Don't use this app - they dont care about you at all.", "Bought premium (little under $9/wk because it was on sale). Was good at first but right now it's not letting me view profiles of people who have liked me (I can see their picture but when I click on them a blank square comes up instead of their profile). Literally the only reason I bought premium was so I could see people who liked me, so it's very frustrating that the feature stopped working. Hopefully it will work again soon. Edit: also not letting me send or view messages right now. :/", 'Very good idea but poor efficiency; is a pity that girls have only 24 hrs to establish a contact... Also, you should put more filters: for example: eyes color, hair color, etc., and stablish options to search by that criteria; for exemple, if I only want to meet people without kids or blonde girls or short (or tall) girls, be able to find those persons easily.', "The premium option is nice, maybe a little expensive for what you get. My issue is that with the premium subscription you run out of people within your filters. But if you're subscription ends you will run out of likes before you run out of people within your filters. Things don't add up properly.", "Even after having premium it doesn't let's text to someone who liked my profile. It clearly showed in best bees match. But it didn't let me text. What a pathetic app. They just want you to keep browsing and keep paying for super swipes or compliments even after buying premium. You will get nothing here. I think they just got some profiles when they launched the app. Might be no longer active because this app doesn't let people text even after liking from both sides.", "Don't recommend, I submitted seven verification photos exactly the way my profile poster was & when I tried to get customer support I've gotten zero response back other than them saying they verified who I am but to try to keep verifying my picture that matches. I paid for the week premium & the app is still stuck in the verification process & will not let me move forward. & they're still trying to charge me of subscription fee. The email I get back from customer service is a auto generated", "Horrible experience - they aren't responding to my emails to restore my lifetime premium membership. Been writing to them since two weeks to restore the unlimited premium subscription that I bought previously, no response to whatsoever, just an auto reply that we've received your email. The worst customer team ever. I don't even know if they'll fix this for me, but I'll continue to follow up."]

title: Dog Breeds: All Dogs Breeds
description:
Dog Breeds App is a complete dog breed encyclopedia that brings you information and photos of hundreds of dog breeds.

This app contains all information about dog breeds: appearance, character, weight, and History. It includes high-definition photos.

Dog Breeds database contains more than 500 dog breeds and their info. Dog lovers find a lot of useful information about their pets. Information about dog contains history, description, health, temperament, appearance.

 Dog breeds App is a product of DogsMart which is the world's 1st only application which deals with sale and purchase of dogs online. If you are a seller of puppies than you can upload the complete description of the puppies your want to sell. The buyers can select from the wide varieties of choices available and get the perfect match of the desired puppies or dogs.

Find out all about dogs you like, and discover which pets are smart, easy to train, healthy, and live the longest.

The characteristics you can use for filtering are: size, kid-friendly, dog-friendly, low shedding, easy to groom, energy level, good health, low barking, intelligence, easy to train, tolerates hot weather and tolerates cold weather;

Do you live in a small apartment and want a dog that will never grow too big? You can filter your search to show only small dogs or any other size of dogs!


Are you worried that your home will be full of fur? Use the filter to find low shedding dog breeds!


You can also search by name, in case you want to find a specific breed!


See dog breed pictures and share them with your friends or family!


Dogs have been selectively bred for thousands of years, sometimes by inbreeding dogs from the same ancestral lines, sometimes by mixing dogs from very different lines. The process continues today, resulting in a wide variety of breeds, hybrids, and types of dogs. As such, dogs are the only animal with such a wide variation in appearance without speciation, "from the Chihuahua to the Great Dane."

The following list uses a wide interpretation of "breed." Breeds are usually categorized by the functional type from which the breed was developed. The basic types are companion dogs, guard dogs, hunting dogs, herding dogs, and working dogs, although there are many other types and subtypes. Breeds listed here may be traditional breeds with long histories as registered breeds, rare breeds with their own registries, or new breeds that may still be under development.

Afador Dog, Affenhuahua Dog, Bouvier Des Ardennes Dog, Australian Cattle Dog, Australian Stumpy Tail Cattle Dog, Belgian Shepherd Dog, Old English SheepDog, Welsh Corgi Cardigan Dog, Welsh Corgi Pembroke Dog, Berger De Beauce Dog, Komondor Dog, Kuvasz Dog, Puli Dog, Pumi Dog, Schipperke Dog, Catalan SheepDog, Shetland SheepDog, Portuguese SheepDog, Briard Dog, Pyrenean Sheepdog - Smooth Faced Dog, Slovakian Chuvach Dog, Collie Rough Dog, German Shepherd Dog, Picardy SheepDog, Bergamasco Shepherd Dog, Dutch Shepherd Dog, Mudi Dog, Polish Lowland SheepDog, Tatra Shepherd Dog, Bearded Collie Dog, Croatian Shepherd Dog, Australian Kelpie Dog, Collie Smooth Dog, Border Collie Dog, Saarloos Wolfhond Dog, Dutch Schapendoes Dog, Majorca Shepherd Dog, South Russian Shepherd Dog, Czechoslovakian WolfDog, Australian Shepherd Dog, White Swiss Shepherd Dog, Romanian Mioritic Shepherd Dog, Romanian Carpathian Shepherd Dog, Lancashire Heeler Dog, Majorca Mastiff Dog, Tosa Dog, Mastiff Dog, Karst Shepherd Dog, Dogo Argentino Dog, Shar Pei Dog, Broholmer Dog, Caucasian Shepherd Dog, Kangal Shepherd Dog, Central Asia Shepherd Dog, Saint Miguel Cattle Dog, Italian Corso Dog, Dogo Canario Dog, Cimarr√≥n Uruguayo Dog, Bosnian and Herzegovinian - Croatian Shepherd Dog, Southeastern European Shepherd Dog, Austrian Pinscher Dog, Dobermann Dog, Giant Schnauzer Dog, Schnauzer Dog, Miniature Schnauzer Dog, German Pinscher Dog, Miniature Pinscher Dog, Affenpinscher Dog, Dutch Smoushond Dog, Russian Black Terrier Dog etc.
summary: Dog Breeds app is a complete dog breed encyclopedia that brings you info of dogs

comments: ['A wonderful and comprehensive study of all dog breeds making this app a vital research tool for the public and veterinarians who need to brush up on breeds unfamiliar to them because of the rarity of contact with that type of dog. It is very well organized and written, as well. Good place to find out about a breed before deciding to purchase or adopt one. Physical descriptions as well as temperament descriptions are quite detailed..', 'Excellent app, still missing several pictures. Neo. Mastiff for example. One star deduction for missing images. Great to help someone learn basics about a breed.', "I don't like I need to use my Google account to login before I can even look at the app, but the information about breeds is nice, the pics are good for generic appearance but better pics could have been chosen.", 'I love the app but please can you add a search bar because whenever i go on the app i have to look through all the breeds for a specific breed and it takes me almost five minutes to find the exact one im looking for . Also please can you add a filter so i can put on how small i want the dog to be how kid/dog friendly and the life span i would love the app even more if these were on. This will be a great help and this is all i did it for This is all i need you to do before i uninstall the app', 'Nice informative app for finding the right pet for you.it has almost all dog breeds with complete information.', 'Best Dog Breeds app to find the which dog breed is best for you. The Dog Breeds - DogsMart app is providing the all details of every dog breed. Below are the some best features in the Dog Breeds app: No Google Ads, Offline feature- only one time login required. Almost 500 Dog Breeds detail, Easy to use, Pocket friendly app - Dog Breeds DogsMart üòÉ', 'Dog Breeds DogsMart application is a simple and easy to use. One of the best app. Great experience. title: Hundeo: Puppy & Dog Training
description:
üê∂ Dog & Puppy Training Made Easy üêï
Don't have a dog trainer or puppy training school with you right now? No problem! Hundeo offers you step-by-step video instructions on the most important topics that a digital dog obedience school can offer you in your pocket. We guide you from puppy to senior with the right content.

300+ Tricks, Games, Recipes and Courses.
Discover a wide range of tricks, games, and recipes for dogs. Get inspiration for your next training session and have fun together. In this app, you can find for example these course topics: Basic Commands, Puppy Basics (Walking the Pup, Potty House Training, Bite inhibition, Puppy Nutrition, Puppy Games, Puppy Commands), Leash Training, Recall Masterclass, How to ignore other dogs on walks, How to behave during a visit, Clicker Course, Dog Impulse control Guide, Health Check at Home, Raw Food Diet, Muzzle Trainer, Calm at Office, New Year's Eve Training, Stop your dog from eating random things, Stop Barking Trainer or Stay Alone Course for Dogs.

Step by Step to Your Goal
We guide you to your goal with our interactive video tutorials.
The tutorials are designed so that you can be successful with just 5 minutes of training a day. It reminds you of your training and when you train successfully, you get a great trophy for your virtual trophy case. In addition to dog training methods, you will also find great activities in the form of pet games and recipes.

Anytime, Anywhere - At Your Own Pace
Out in the park or garden with no reception? No problem. You can download content and use it offline.

New Daily
Daily free quizzes, tricks, games, recipes and courses carefully selected for you. Tailored to you and your breed. (We have 285 dog breeds like Labrador, French Bulldog, Pug, Doberman, Chihuahua)

Playfully to Success
To keep you motivated, you get new challenges every day and earn flames and trophies. 

Individual Profile
Create a profile for your puppy, dog, or even multiple pets and keep track of what you have accomplished and what you still need to practice.

Connect With Others
Have you learned some cool dog or puppy tricks and want to compare yourself with others? Invite your friends or other members of our community to compare your achievements and watch videos of other dogs and puppies.

Your Favorites
Keep track and create your own favorites list for easy access.

Clicker and Whistle Always With You
With a clicker, you always have the right tone with you. A clicker is the most efficient way to teach your puppy tricks and exercises.

Trusted
This app was developed in collaboration with professional dog experts and pet trainers. You can be sure that the exercises will really help you.

Support
If you have any questions about Hundeo or your account, please contact our customer support: support@hundeo.com

Hundeo Plus Membership
To unlock all the features, you can upgrade to ‚Äòhundeo Plus‚Äô and choose between the following subscriptions:
1 month
1 year

Terms and Conditions: https://www.hundeo.com/en/toc/
Privacy policy: https://www.hundeo.com/en/contact/data-protection/

comments: ["The app is pretty good and easy to work around. My only problem is that I have to be on a subscription or premium plan in order to access most of the stuff. People who go to apps for dog training don't really have the money, so they're not going to be able to go on to the premium plan to get access to most of the app. Other than that, it's a good app", "For weeks under maintenance, no training plans available Update: I was not using an old version but I have Adguard on my phone. Seems like the app does not work if it's routed through Adguard...", "I honestly enjoy this training tips it's extremely helpful to me .", 'easy to follow! works well', 'This looks like a really cool app, and I was very excited to use it with my twin cavapoo puppies. But I was dismayed that after I created an account it said that there were only 7 days of a free trial and then I would have to pay for the app and would be automatically billed for it. Beyond not impressed with this bait and switch for what is advertised as a free app. I deleted my account immediately, and I better not be charged in a week.', "I just downloaded & has all the selections of different trainings, tips & tricks. looks like alot of information needed ..HOWEVER, I am needing something to be done QUICK...instead of learning one tip or trick at a time.. it wants to give me ONE lesson one day at a time...I have a dog with separation anxiety & will not stop barking.. barks all night & throughout the day at times.PLEAAE HELP.... I'm still trying other apps as well for the dog barking..whistling apps etc.. I can't afford the prem", 'fun and easy!', "Good app but my dog won't listen to me when I teach her high-five she only listen to me when it's paw or games,‚òπÔ∏è", 'Epic I just downloaded I tryed to get her to lie down but she just looked down but well work on it.', "Not Free at all!!! Advertised as free but the only 'free' part is an introduction to each lesson, the introduction only tells you what you will get out of that lesson and gives no advice at all. Don't waste your time unless you want to pay.", 'I tried it with my dog and definitely got results, the tricks and games are great fun for my doggy and honestly cheap for a year of home-training!', 'I love the great video collection. It is also good that there are not only educational videos but also about dog health.', 'Simple, easy to follow tips and tutorials. Helped me finally to get my puppy to sit and control those impulses!', "so far the app is very helpful, Roxie has already picked up on 2 new tricks! She's such a smart little girl!", 'Good free version', 'Very good and helpful I have a young dog and have long been looking for a solution that helps. I really like the step-by-step video tutorials.', 'wow it taught my dog to stay when I went some where yet he has separation anxiety wow thanks', 'it really helped me trane my dog not that good, but it is not the app it is the dogü•∞', 'Amazing app should use for sure only thing you need to pay it would be amazimg to gave it for free for some people it would be really useful', "my dog is a puppy and she doesn't now any tricks so I need help", 'tried free version for 7 days, forgot about it and they charged me not even month but for 1 year. Looks like scum.', 'Great for teach dogs tricks,and great recipes so over all brilliant app(my fav trick was little heart‚ô°‚ô°)', "Very nice app but one thing I don't like that is there is not Indian spitz bread option.I hope you will add it.", "DO NOT DOWNLOAD. THE APP DOESN'T WORK MOST OF THE TIME. ONCE YOU SUBSCRIBE YOU CAN'T CANCEL IT. IT'LL CHARGE YOU EVERY MOUTH AND THERE IS NO WAY TO GET OUT OF IT.", 'I recommend this app because it teaches your dog commands that you want them to listen to and it also help my dog sit shake and pound it which is a good thing', "Couldn't even get started. Just got to the setup your account and even after I did, didn't move on to the next stage.", 'The right thing for me as a dog owner Very well-developed app for dog owners. A well done app. I like it.', 'Installed in German . Could not change to English Language', "anyway we can get Great Pyrenees tips and tricks?!? found my lab, river, profile but can't set up my charlie bears just yet bc there isn't a bread set up for him yet.", 'wonderful app! Thank you so much, it taught my dog, Doc, how to stay', 'It has amazing trick ideas and amazing healthy recipes for your dog üê∂üêïüê©üê∂üêïüê©üêïüê∂', 'so good helps my dog learn so many new things', "It's nice but there was no breed option for English shepherd i hope you add that someday", 'Not able to login. Some error popping up', 'I know this is The only review but trust me,this is The Best app ever! My dog learned so much tricks from there!üòªüòª‚ù§Ô∏è\u200dü©π', 'The app looks good , i only gave it 4 stars because I have not used the training methods on my 4 dogs yet but I will try it tomorrow.', "Save yourself some money. There's far BETTER programs out there.", 'good for most partsüôÇ', 'This good is very very interesting ‚ò∫Ô∏è and I am very happy to using this app üòä and dog too thankyou so much', "Very good app I love it but I tried making a profile for my dad's dog but there's no American bulldog but my dog works he is a pug"]

title: Dog Scanner: Breed Recognition
description: The Dog Scanner app will identify your dog's breed reliably in just a few seconds! Besides taking a picture, you can also record a video or upload an image from your gallery. Got a mixed breed? No problem, the Dog Scanner app also recognizes mixed breeds! We provide you with detailed data and interesting facts about the different breeds of your mixed breed dog. No dog around? Doesn‚Äôt matter! The Dog Scanner app also recognizes humans: Simply scan yourself, your friends, your family or the people around you and find out which dogs you resemble the most! ------ NEW! Become a part of our Dog Scanner community! Share your results and compare them to the results of the community! Upload pictures of your favorite dog to our Social Feed and share them with other dog lovers! Have a look at the profiles and photos of other users, like and comment on posts from our dog community and filter them by date or popularity! Additionally, you can easily share your posts with your friends by simply sending a picture directly from the Dog Scanner app. ------ NEW! Catch all dog breeds and become an expert! Catch all the dog breeds with our Gamification feature ‚Äì just like in Pok√©mon Go! Master the challenges, earn virtual treats and become a true dog expert! Compete with your friends or users from the community and climb to the top of our ranking list! ------ All dog breeds in the Dog Scanner app! The Dog Scanner app currently identifies more than 370 different dog breeds, including all breeds officially recognized by the F√©d√©ration Cynologique Internationale (FCI) and even some more! Our comprehensive database with information and pictures of all dog breeds (including the unofficial ones) can also be accessed completely without scanning! Give us feedback on the Dog Scanner app! Let us know if the dog‚Äôs breed has been correctly identified. If not, you will get useful tips to improve your own results. If you also indicate which dog breed is in the picture, you help us to enhance our software since the app automatically learns how to provide even more accurate outcomes. Also suggest or vote for (unofficial) dog breeds that you want us to add to the app in the future! Get your premium upgrade! With our premium version, the app will no longer show ads and your results will be available faster. Furthermore, you can now choose whether your dog breeds should be recognized rather quickly or with higher accuracy. With the premium version, scanning dogs is also possible in offline mode, so you no longer need an active internet connection to identify their breeds. With the optional in-app purchase of our premium version, you will also help to support this app. ------ Find us on social media! On our social media channels we provide you with the most beautiful dog pictures from the community. You will also find many interesting facts about man's best friend. Furthermore, we will keep you updated on all new added features of the Dog Scanner app in the future. * Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dogscanner_app * Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DogScannerApp * Twitter: https://twitter.com/dogscanner_app ------ Just give it a shot! Dog recognition as easy as it gets! Despite the small app size you will get all features and be able to identify a dog‚Äôs breed or get access to our extensive database at any time! Before you consider getting an expensive DNA test, simply scan your dog with the app and the dog breed will automatically be determined within seconds! Download the Dog Scanner app now!
summary: See a dog, but don't know its breed? Just take a picture and find out!

comments: ["The app itself is not bad as a bit of fun, although suspect it isn't very accurate with mixed breeds. The number of ads makes it unusable though, as there seems to be one every 20 seconds and if you close one of the small ads, a full page one immediately appears. I may have purchased the ad free version if I had a chance to try the app for a bit longer, but am not prepared to watch that many ads just to decide if I like it.", "To say the ads are intrusive is an understatement. Every action you take gets an ad and the interface is similar to those websites that have 30 download now buttons trying to get you to download a virus. The TikTok ad is app-breaking. It is unskippable with no X to click. Even opening it still takes you back to the ad. There's no way around it but to exit the app. I did manage to get one picture in and it identified the breed incorrectly. Why would they think we'd pay for a pro version? 0/5. ;(", "I got the perfect shot and it correctly identified the dachshund in my dog. It all just depends on the perfect shot (all you have to do is just take a side picture of your dog looking at you helps). It just should lower the analysis time and have a better accuracy when people take pictures of the owners dogs. But I love it even if they didn't do that.", "actually surprised me! sometimes it fails to identify a common breed but then somehow it manages to CORRECTLY dentify random cross breeds. obviously the picture will play a part in how accurate the results are, but even a perfect pic might not get the right result cuz obviously identifying a breed by a pic alone isn't an exact science and one dogs can look like one think but be 100% proven to be something completely different, appearances can be misleading. cool app though", "I would definitely recommend this app. Out of all of the apps I tried, this one was bang on identifying a 4 week old puppy we rescued. the accuracy isn't 100% but pretty damn close. For anyone using this app, make sure you use more than one picture to see how many times it recognizes a specific breed, and then do your research. This is a great app to use to give you a lead on a breed, and the rest is up to you.", "Not sure to give it 2 or 3 stars. They did well to get 1m downloads so respect for that because it's main functionality which is the scan is average at best. They even openly admit on the app that the top 1 accuracy is 71%. This is a pretty bad result. If you like bells and whistles then this app is for you. If you would like to get proper identification - there are better apps around.", "1-27-21 App problems have been fixed. Great job! Update 9/27/20-Developer updated app. When scanning photo(s) from gallery the app no longer works properly but constantly flips back into camera mode. Unfortunate. From 5 to 1 star and deleting app. Will check back periodically to see if it's fixed. 7/31/20-So far, a truly wonderful and innovative app. I'm really enjoying it.", "Fun and pretty accurate readings based on a photo, or many different photos together to cover all bases. It was right on on my dogs and has a lot of info on specific breeds. I scanned many different photos of my dogs and it gave me the right answer with details on breed, or breeds. Very cool and fun. I was glued for over an hour playing around with this app. I don't think I'll delete it yet.", "This isn't a bad app at all. I've only used it for about four of my assorted mongrels so far, but it knew my hairy Bulgarian dog was a mix of various Eastern European shepherds. I don't know her origins, but the dogs it suggested seemed pretty close. Plausible enough for passing curiosity, anyway. I wouldn't want to settle an argument with it, but it's a bit of fun.", "Its something different and some what funny. But very unreliable. So unreliable that I am willing to bet it get's the dog breed every time unless ypu owm a pure bred. Again I am not hating the app or developers. Hopefully they can creat default ways to take pictures this way it is more accurate. Especially when considering am entire skeletal structure in a picture.", "the free version is nearly impossible to use bc the amount of ads. I mean, I've never seen anything like it. Waaaaaaaayyyy too many ads. pretty much every 3 click activates the same Temu ad for a washing machine ü´§", "I love it! I've been waiting to find something like this for years It's pretty spot on. I think it's cool that it can recognize mix breeds. I can't say for sure how accurate it is because my dogs are a mix of at least 2 but probably 3 or 4 different breeds, but the app results agree almost perfectly with our best guesses for both dogs, so i think it's great.", 'Absolutely awesome and how do you do it? I was very easily able to scan several dogs in our family (must sit still 5 seconds) with the app. The answer is perfect especially for Heinz 57 and somewhat mixed breeds. It gives a breakdown in percentages with sample photos to support their analysis. Suggest you take a FULL profile scan and not facial close up. Highly recommend this app!!!', "Pretty cool app. Just wanted ideas of what my dog could be mixed with as she looks like a larger version of a heeler. The only negative is the intensity of the ads. I'm fine with free apps showing ad banners, or occasionally a short ad, but press ANY button and you're stuck with a 30s ad video AND the post-ad promotional poster that makes you wait to press the 'x'. Good for a one time use it if you have patience, or probably if you pay", "I kept being interrupted by ads, and when I finally reached Dog Scan, there was nothing...NOTHING to show me how to use it!!!. It also crashed 3 times while I was on there. Don't bother with this app, its annoying and VERY frustrating!!!üò°üò°üò°", 'If you give it a reasonable photograph, it does seem to come up with reasonable matches. I tested three mixed breed adult dogs of unknown origin, but from the same litter. One of the three looks different from the other two. The app gave me the same sorts of answers for each dog. Dutch shepherd. I tested multiple photographs. The variation was not as great as I expected it to be.', "It's a good idea, but it's not accurate; It seems like developers are on the right path as far as using images submitted and asking users to correct what breed the scanned dog actually is for future recognition abilities of this app.... but it has never been right :/ I tried multiple dogs that I know.", "Could be useful to rescue groups and shelters. Best results when using a full view picture without much else in the photo. Not useful for some mixed breeds. Others have provided good feedback. I've tested some shelter dogs, comparing their guess to the tool suggestion. Many times I've agreed with the app over the shelter guess.", "The app is pretty good so far. The only time I can say for a fact it was wrong was when I scanned my rat terrier. She's a runt and sickly, so she looks more like a chihuahua. It scanned her as that, but it's a common mistake, so not one that surprised me. Aside from that, it gave me good insight on what my other dogs might be. Only issue is that the video ads can be intrusive. Went from one every 10min to 3 in a minute.", 'I have 2 poodles. One everyone thinks is not a poodle due to the texture of her hair. The scanner guessed both breeds correctly. I see complaints about the ads but it comes with the territory of a free app. Stop complaining or pay for the premium version.', "Dogs don't like loud sudden ad sounds in their face while getting a photo taken. These adds are full-screen and can't be backed out of. Unexpected startling ad sounds is not too smart for a pet friendly app.", "I had an incredibly loud and intrusive ad and it had no obvious X or mute, pressing what looked like an escape route forcefully opened my app store, once I went back to the app, the advertisement was still stuck on my screen, now it had an X and I pressed it, but it took me right back to the store again. Double kill. I don't think I trust this app and I'm deleting this immediately, it couldn't correctly identify my dog either.", "This app is pretty cool not to sure how accurate these kind really are. I took a picture of one of our dogs and got my friend in the picture and it kind of confused the app so it gave me an idea to take a picture just of my friend & the result was partly correct when it said human the very funny thing was it said the larger percentage was Great Dane. We laughed so hard. I still smile when I think about it. They do say sometimes we tend to resemble each other-thing is we don't have a Great Dane.", 'I have three foster puppies from the same litter, all were totally different. Also, took different pictures with same outcome. Different breed, every time.  Also took another picture of my dog (we had a dna test on him) again with different results that were completely different. It‚Äôs a good thing the app is free.', "It doesn't seem very accurate because I scanned my dog at three different angles and I got three different results and two of the same angle and two different results and not one of the breeds, out of all the five times I got results, did any of the results have one of the same as the others. So I couldn't even get a good guestimate.", 'I was impressed. scanner is most impressive. was able to get clear and focused images of dog scanned dog three times and he was identified as the same breed each time and the percent of account increased each time until 98%. Yes GREAT APP. üëç', "It's so cute! But besides that, it's fairly accurate so long as you do several photos from different angles. Sometimes depending on the features that certain breeds have, a weird angle could change the entire results.", 'Great fun! Used this app on my "pavement special" rescued dogs and came up with some interesting results. Not that accurate, but I won\'t hold that against this app as dogs can be difficult to identify, especially if they are bouncing around when you try to scan them - something the app manages to do well. Like I said great fun, informative on breeds and I enjoy using it.', "The app has been correct. I clicked incorrect on one of them because the husky breed was off but that's not a surprise because the breeds are so closely linked. a second scan of the same dog with body without the face came up with the closer mix. I'm very impressed and happy with the results. I also love the info that comes with the breed.", 'As someone else said it\'s good for entertainment value. App said my purebred Mastiff (rescued retired breeder) was Mixed breed and gave FOUR different breeds, most of them pretty off. Apparently my other 2 rescues are both Australian Kelpies, one of them a purebred - don\'t think so. [EDIT: have to eat my words - I searched black/tan kelpies and my "purebred" rly matches the look!] Using the app was nice enough (except for the ad every single time). It just doesn\'t have superb accuracy. Yet?', "it's kinda fun. I'm not sure I would pay for the app but it's fun to scan my dogs and see what it comes up with. I believe it scans the dog then runs the photo through its database of pictures and compares it to them. it pulls out the ones that look most like the dog depending on the angle of the scan you did. The first scan I did of my 3mth old puppy seemed pretty accurate. I will be trying my other dogs too. It also has a cat scanner option.", "I've only just downloaded this, but it correctly figured out the breeds of all three of my dogs, even from images where they weren't facing the camera, and figured out that my cat was, in fact, a cat when I tried to trick it. Now, none of those would be hard for a human to figure out, but I am genuinely impressed an app could manage it.", '4 and a half stars Nifty little app. I love animals, especially dogs, so I can defnitely see how having dog scanner will come in handy. Whenever hanging out with family and/or friends you can turn it into a fun game. Knowing dogs as well as I do I can see myself winning a lot, lol. Not only do you have the fun factor of playing a game, its an educational tool as well.', "Love, LOVE, L-O-V-E this app. and, I haven't even had it for 24 hours! I have been using a similar app, for several months. Yet, so far, Dog Scanner is, Leaps & Bounds above the competition. I mean, you guys are...KILLING IT! Period. I purchased the premium version of Dog Scanner. Main reason was to eliminate Ads. (Thanks, Ads-No-More). I was, also, impressed by the amount of, factually accurate, breed specific info (contained-within-the app.) Kudos-to-You, Dog Scanner. Your product ROCKS!üòãüôÉüòú", "This app is interesting, and insightful. I've only tried it with my dog, which was an unknown mix of breeds until I used this app. Very fun and surprisingly accurate for how many poor angles and lightnings I used in the pictures. The ads in app are very small and do not get in the way of using the app (thank you!!)", "I tried 4 different photos of the same dog, all clear pictures that included his face. (The dog is a stray mutt that showed up.) Results varied widely. Side views of the head seemed to work best. It doesn't work that great with mixes, but is still helpful in that it can suggest possible breeds present in the ancestry of your mutt. Then you can google those breeds specifically to see more pictures. Easier than combing thru photos online, but not as good as asking your vet, is my opinion.", 'Just downloaded the app, from one I saw so far it seems excellent. Obviously ads all the time....normal. What I would like to see is improvement on detailed info..like weight range and longevity. For me this seems like an excellent app for people who see a dog they like and interested in getting one, so providing this kind of information would bring greater interest in your app.', "Awful app. Ads whenever you press anything, can't figure out how to close the ads, cluttered and too complicated. Waste of time.", "Highly Accurate - Don't listen to the naysayers. Often times when people get inaccurate results, they are using a bad picture with bad lighting. This app has accurately identified over 100+ breeds as I volunteer at an animal shelter and have used it to identify both purebred and mixed dogs. Whenever it got the breed wrong, changing the angle of the pic, adding better lighting and finessing the overall picture - resulted in a correct identification of the mutt at hand. Enjoy! A great app indeed!!", 'Really cool idea for an app. One thing that would make the results higher quality would be to allow users to upload multiple photos from different positions, then run each photo through the service and average the results.']

title: Dog Hotel Tycoon
description:
Become a dog hotel tycoon, and create a world for your dog guests to enjoy!

CREATE A WORLD FOR YOUR DOG GUESTS TO ENJOY!
Start with a small dog hotel in a suburban area, and improve it to become the first 5+ star dog hotel! Create areas for your dogs to take naps, eat delicious snacks, play with each other, swim, excercise and much more! Anything to ensure the satisfaction of your dog guests!

WELCOME DOGS FROM ALL AROUND THE WORLD!
Become a dog hotel tycoon and accept more breeds as you grow your hotel, such as Corgi, Dachshund, Pug, Samoyed, Poodle, German Shepherd, Labrador, French Bulldog, English Bulldog, Basset Hound, Chiuahua, Chow Chow, Beagles, Shiba Inu, and many more. Each and every single dog will have their own unique character, behavior, wants and needs; and it is up to you to satisfy them!

TAKE YOUR DOGS TO DAILY DOG EVENTS!
Each day, you'll be able to take your dogs to the daily Dog Show, which is a physical obstacle challenge that will test the health & fitness of your dogs! 
There will also be a new Dog Quiz waiting for you each day, which will test your knowledge about dogs as well as teaching you interesting facts about them!

FEATURES
‚òÖ Easy to play game for every animal lover!
‚òÖ Cute Dogs with unique characteristics and lifelike behavior!
‚òÖ More than 80 dogs to have as guests, and more to come!
‚òÖ Fun rooms and items for your dogs to enjoy!
‚òÖ Send your dogs to Dog Shows!
‚òÖ Learn about dogs and earn rewards with the daily Dog Quiz!

If you love dogs, and incremental idle clicker games, you will love idle Dog Hotel Tycoon. As with all idle clicker games, you will never run out of things to do!

This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. If you are having any issues with the game or have any feedback, you can always reach us at support@filgames.com
summary: Become a dog hotel tycoon, and create a world for your dog guests to enjoy!

title: Dog Sweetie - My Puppy
description:
„ÄêBEST IPET ON YOUR MOBILE DEVICE„Äë
‚òÖBest mobile game of the first China Mobile Internet fist award.
‚òÖExcellent game of China app game contest.
‚òÖTop class dog raising experience. Virtual dog for everyone. 

„ÄêMain Feature„Äë
‚òÖBreed collection: More than 30 breeds in the game, even Tibet Mastiff included!
‚òÖDog care: Feed,water,bath,touch.anything. you can even hug your dog!
‚òÖTricks training: Teach your dogs to learn more than 20 tricks! Even including Gangnam style!
‚òÖTop class DIY: Dress your dogs, Decorate your house, Give your dog tattoo.Best of all,you can try everything before you purchase them.
‚òÖInteraction: Interact with friends, help them or steal their coins,your choice.Get married and have puppies.
‚òÖChallenge: Fight on the street to earn the ranks. You have No.1 dogs.Bravo!

„ÄêContact„Äë
‚òÖSupportÔºösupport@lonfun.com

Our Photo Verification tool is in place to give you confidence that the person you‚Äôre talking to looks like their profile picture. To ensure our members are who they say they are, we also provide a phone number and social media account verification. ‚Ä¢ With our SmartPick‚Ñ¢ you can get better matches based on compatibility and preferences. Once you find someone you want to chat with, try one of our icebreakers, write a message*or even send a gift*! READY. SET. DATE. No more senseless swipes: download Zoosk dating app and get ready, because meeting someone is just a tap away. If you decide to upgrade or purchase one of our subscriptions here‚Äôs what you should know: ‚Ä¢ All subscriptions and upgrades like coins automatically renew unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period without any limitations. ‚Ä¢ Turn off the auto-renewal through your account settings and your subscription and/or upgrades will expire at the end of their term ‚Ä¢ To learn more, read our Terms of Use Agreement: http://www.zoosk.com/tos and ‚Ä¢ Check our FAQs: http://zoosk.com/help. ‚Ä¢ See our Privacy Policy: www.zoosk.com/privacy and online dating safety guide at https://www.zoosk.com/safety. comments: ["The account setup is great but the app itself functionality-wise is a mess. I can't even like a profile without it telling me that I need to verify my account even though I did it, multiple times via email. It's the same with the video verification as well I submit but then the same page appears over and over. I can't use basic functions, It's because of this that I won't be using this app. There's also a very limited selection as well as I've been seeing the same profiles over and over again.", "I heard good things about this app. I went and purchased the shortest subscription among only 3 choices it offered to handcuff me to in terms of subs. (3mo). I'd have liked a weekly option to try it without the long commitment. There's nothing wrong with the app itself. Only, I keep seeing the same online users over and over. After reaching out to dozens of them not a single one replied. The only good thing I've found is there are no bots. I cancelled the sub but still have over a month left.", 'The app is a complete waste of time unless you are willing to pay their monthly fees to see who liked you or send & read messages. So, unless you pay AND the person you wanted to communicate with also paid for the subscription you will be wasting your time. Also, if you do happen to join, you will see a green dot on a few profiles indicating they have logged on within the past few days. There are very few even when I expand the search criteria. An absolute waste of time.', 'I have been on here 2 months.....I paid to be able to talk and maybe meet someone. I am constantly having to verify myself. No one responds to messages or likes. The profiles for the smartpicks, you can barely see the pics people put up. I constantly have to change my search preferences and no preferences for the smartpicks. Honestly, the app really sucks!!!!', 'The app continuously crashes after about 2 mins of use. Very frustrating! Carousel is a useless tool as it doesn\'t take any of your preferences into account and you can\'t see how far away some is when choosing to "like" or not. If someone lives 500 miles away I wouldn\'t "like" them.', 'So frustrating, who are your developers and ux people??? Has to be one of the worst dating apps in navigation and usage... Same girls keep popping up first so you have to keep scrolling through them to get to the new ones, this is a 10 minute coding fix and no one thinks this is a problem??? And two options, remove conversation and remove connection, what the heck... And then some girls you only get one of those choices even when you have written them... Just horrible quality control', "Same notifications are being shown all the time. In Smartpick, you can't look at photos, only a tiny thumbnail of 1 picture. So how are you supposed to choose and teach the algorithm accurately about what you like?", "Customer service was good when I complained about a couple of things but other than that that's about as far as it goes. If anybody's actually real and close to you they certainly don't want to chat or me. I sent out 67 messages got a response from one. Pay the extra for premium messaging so they could answer me without worrying about it and they still didn't do that. Just like all the others it all comes down to money nonexistent profiles. Pretty much a waste of time.", "It's a free app you pay for... Ots free to download, setup etc then to even message yoi have to pay , the UI is absolute trash. Should not be allowed to have apps this predatory. So after trying it further just seems more and more like 99% if the interactions are fake. If not 30 seconds after I like someone they like back instantly but anyone I pass doesn't like it screams some marketing BS. Also ¬£25PM? For any kind of basic app use? Yeah you need shutting down.", "Set up to keep you swiping, recommends users and hitting the red x does not make them go away so even if you just see the user profile Zoosk will alert them that you're in fact visiting their profile. So it looks like a bunch of people are viewing you. Carousel mode sucks because you have to say yes or no based on one pic and not able to visit their profile, smart pick sucks for the same reason, and the next date live feature is like something from some kind of onlyfans nightmare. DELETED", "This app is not worth it. I tried the 1 month purchase and I am extremely disappointed. No one ever response and the same few memeber for the example keep looking at my profile but nothing more. Hey I might not be the most attractive but come on. No activity anywhere .No one ever online it was a waste of money don't waste your hard earned money on this specific app.", 'The style works well. Carousel as others say, has potential, but broken. Why would I want to meet someone 500 miles away? App needs a search choice on activity, mostly dear in my demographic. Wish I knew how it worked better before wasting money subscribing. WE NEED A SEARCH OPTION FOR ACTIVITY ON APP!', "Hi good day to all. My name is Avion and this is the worst experience that I have had on this app, as a matter of fact, I have an account that can't be erased, thanks to someone who is using it. I have pressed unsubscribed, wrote to customer service, and still it hasn't been deleted. I find it very disturbing that this company has refused to delete my account, that someone else is using, only to their benefit (whose name is Sarah and apparently lives in Houston and I am from the Caribbean).", "I've met some good people on Zoosk, but your experience is probably dependent on your location. The Carousel is the worst. It matches based on pictures, does not filter for distance, and the app counts a Carousel view as a profile view. Otherwise, it's one of the better apps.", "Too many annoying notifications digging for clicks. Don't give you any way to choose which ones you get so you get 9/10 useless notifications just to get the one useful notification. Its like a predatory ad with their click bait. Oh ... and turning off notifications doesn't actually stop them. They just remove the information and send them anyway. Get some better coders.", "My account cannot be deleted. I can only deactivate. This is an absolute disgrace. Who do you think you are, keeping people's data after they've removed consent? There's a vague reference online to having to email the company to get your account deleted. No one should have to do this. Any other app just lets you delete whenever you want in app. Also, it's impossible to find an email address to contact! Oh, and FYI, I'm deleting because the app in general is terrible.", "Can't msg/reply or see msg unless you pay. They edit your bio taking out just the words they don't like. I've X people and still see them pop up. Any dating site that wants the cost of a phone card just to msg someone is unreasonable. They have the option of paying for the year for cheaper per month, but if they did a good job no one should search that long. The view profile is üôÉ scroll every pic before seeing info / bio if there even is a bio.", "Changing my review from two stars to one. Too bad there isn't a zero stars option. DO NOT WASTE YOUR MONEY ON THIS APP! This app constantly crashes and I have to reinstall every time I want to use it. All they want is your money. I paid for one month and still can't read messages from other users. If I decline or dismiss someone they'll show up the very next day. Most of the profiles that are too good to be true are bots. Don't walk away from this app, RUN!!!", "Horrible interface. Doesn't limit distance or necessarily show distance to potential matches in all is modes. Not very clear. Also seems to nickel and dime you after you have a subscription. Wouldn't recommend at all", 'Issue when you scroll over those who have "Viewed Me" it registers to the other person that you\'ve browsed their profile when you\'ve just scrolled past. This generates confusion as people think you\'re interested in them if you have to scroll past. Please fix this up so that the wrong message is not received.', 'There was no option to chat with anyone without having a paid subscription, so I went ahead & paid for 3 months, just to find out that\'s not the worst part. Men who I "X" out, indicating I\'m not interested in keep popping up & keep messaging me. Some getting increasingly more hostile that I\'m not responding. When I disconnect from matches, they still show up in my search, so I get to look at men who have ghosted me after dates. Overall I\'m displeased.', 'In my opinion, it seems like a scam , I have a team of people who check if these apps are legit , and it seems like some of the profiles are not legitimate. The same , you need to buy credits to chat with people , even when subbed , if you by credits , seem like it either an Ai , or a paid actor that response immediately, please comment if you had similar experience , having to by credits is a red flag lots of sites use the same model , this is all in my opinion.', 'I used to enjoy this service before covid. Now, there are tons of inactive accounts, I know for sure I used to date some of these ladies who are now moved or in a relationship. I wish they required you to long on to keep the account active and disable those accounts who havent login for years. Hardly anyone responds to you. You have to pay just to message anyone or pay for the feature to let people message you back. My area has no members who are active. I felt baited to pay for a subscription.', "It's okay.. I'm truly wishing that the possibilities of dating these amazing interesting guys, just happen to live a very long distance from me... Sad! So, I'm willing to travel a bit.. but it's going to be challenging. I'm hoping this could work out & I find my partner to grow old with, make some wonderful memories.", 'Pretty good app overall. However, Carousel is a totally worthless and distracting but prominent aspect. Who can pick who they "like" without a location? This is after all a "dating app" and if a person lives too far away to "date" what the heck difference does it make? If a member lists the maximum distance they are willing to consider, the app should respect that even if it means there are only a few matches. I can always change my search criteria.', "If I x out someone...they shouldn't keep popping up. Give new people!!! Few glitches have been solved...(6/23) Wish I would have read reviews first. Friend of mine met her husband on here so had to try it. *Click a notification and it doesn't take you to it. *People 500+ miles away! *when you back up on the page it takes you to the home screen rather than who you were looking at.", "It's extremely frustrating to be connected with people so far away. I have my search preference for 50 miles but it still shows me people much farther away. I hate Carousel! You can't see how far they are. I have blocked multiple members because of distance but they keep appearing in my search and also on carousel.", "Yeah, this site sucks. You pay the subscription, but you still have to pay for everything else. You see the same people on your searches. It doesn't tell you if the members even use their account, so it's full of unused accounts. I've seen the same people that probably haven't been on for months. You have to pay to see if someone reads your message. No native american ethnicity choice. The flaws are countless.", 'August 13 2023 So far, this has been a brutal experience. I just joined last night and bought a membership plan. But every time I tried to contact someone, it said, "Subscribe to send." I checked my bank & the payment went through. What the hell?! Now, this morning, I\'m getting messages saying I have to have internet to use the app. Again, what the hell?! I sent an email about the situation, but you guys are taking your sweet time to respond. I\'m so turned off by this! Just give my money back!', "Tried the site out for a month, it would have been smarter for me to flush my money down the toilet! This is the absolutely worst dating site if you ask me and I've tried a few of them. You keep getting interest from women you do not want to get interest from! And you see them over and over and over again. There are far too many things wrong with Zoosk for me to detail, the best advice I can give is don't waste your money or your time.", "Some hiccups sometimes you can't use it freely or are able to see the profiles when is important. Make sure you are talking to a real person, be open to make so friends and who knows. You might be able to find the person that you are looking for!", "Miserable user experience. They charge too much for what you get and constantly ask for more money. There is no way to search for new users without going through the hundreds of users you already have seen. Most users don't respond, which makes me wonder if they are real accounts. Do bot install. Stay away!", "It's not bad however, the amount of fake profiles is unfortunate yet, this is my 3rd time back because out of say 100, 2 that I've met which each turned into a relationship that lasted over several yrs were amazing & worth it. In fact I'm still friends w then after our relationship ended. ü§∑üèª\u200d‚ôÇÔ∏è", "This is about the worst dating app I've used. Hardly any matches in my area. Many of the daily Smart Picks are 100 miles away from me! Those I have matched with don't want to engage in a back and forth conversation. So frustrating!", "Paid for a one month subscription and still denied access to perks of a subscription. Why pay for something when I'm getting the same deal for free? I definitely won't be subscribing again or will I'll be keeping my account active.", 'App is okay. Routinely gives you "views" to keep you interacting with the app though those people may not be actively viewing your profile. The carousel portion is frustrating as you can\'t see the person\'s location and their proximity to you. Lots of "likes" from people way too far away. Met a really good guy on the app and I\'m grateful for that. Watch out for fake profiles/scammers.', 'Terrible app. It constantly states it has no internet connection. It does! All the time. So, I have to uninstall, then reinstall. Absolute pain!', 'WASTE OF TIME AND MONEY! Terrible site. Messages keep failing and being deleted. Site keeps locking up. Customer service is not fixing it. Keeps showing same people even after Ive said no dismiss. Cant block the creeps. Does not work. WASTE OF MONEY! No way to get refund for garbage app.', 'Literally liars. Don\'t fall for it. This app fabricated a message from a profile I liked so I got a message notification. I pay to see the message and it\'s "Thanks for the greeting! Send me a message to start chatting!"', "If you tried to make a worse dating app than this I don't think you could. From fake profiles to delayed messages to would you like to pay extra to see if a message you sent has been read by recipient. Garbage in every way. 0 stars. Designed to keep you paying and paying and paying. Originally a Facebook product. ."]

title: Dog Evolution: Idle Merge Game
description:
If you‚Äôre a dog person and think you know everything about man‚Äôs best friend, your world is about to be rocked! Mix puppy breeds like you‚Äôve never seen before and discover a whole new canine dimension that will leave you barking in such awe: the possibilities are much wow!

Dachshunds, beagles, corgies and retrievers are so last week. Evolved dogs should have an extra eye or two so they can watch over their human friends more efficiently, or a handy horn just in case they get into the odd bar skirmish with a mutant unicorn. It‚Äôs your duty to let the dogs out and help them evolve!

DOGE FEATURES
‚Ä¢ Pantheon: a new place for supreme beings to look down on us mortals and laugh at our misery
‚Ä¢ Impostors: watch out for impostors trying to steal the spotlight from the puppies

HOW TO PLAY
‚Ä¢ Drag and drop similar puppies to create new mysterious doges
‚Ä¢ Use dog eggs to earn coins, buy new creatures and make even more money
‚Ä¢ Alternatively, fiercely tap a rabbit to make coins pop from their eggs

HIGHLIGHTS
‚Ä¢ Different stages and many dog species to discover
‚Ä¢ A mind-blowing story with surprising twists
‚Ä¢ The unexpected mix of creature evolution dynamics and incremental clicker games
‚Ä¢ Doodle-like illustrations
‚Ä¢ Various possible endings: find your destiny
‚Ä¢ No dogs were harmed in the making of this game, only developers

The dog days have just begun! Much fun such wow!

Please note! This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. Some features and extras mentioned in the description may also have to be purchased for real money.
summary: Combine mutant dog breeds and find out just how wacky puppies can get!

comments: ['Pretty fun, just a bit repetitive but I love it', "I enjoy the app it's cute and it's nice to pass the time, but it's kind of difficult to play a game and genuinely enjoy it when it crashes every single time you play an ad unwillingly. I'll just be in the middle of tapping my dogs and then an ad will play and crash the entire app so I have to reopen it every single time an ad plays Please fix this problem", "I love this game!!!!! its so addicting! who ever is reading this,you should get the game. I've been playing for hours. And it is helpful when your on the go or having no wifi,you cam still play the amazing app!!!! I never really got any ads. the only time i had a ad is when i tried getting more diamond diamonds.", "It's really fun and addicting. I could play for hours and hours, maybe even days. The genius who made this game blows my mind. I can't wait to download more games like this fantastic one. I only have had this game for a little, but I already üíó it! When I am playing it on my phone even my dog sits and looks at the screen. I üíó playing this game in a frantic time like this. I can't have a minute were I'm not playing, thinking about it, or talking about it! This game makes me feel ü§™üòãüòç. I üíó it!", "It's a good time waster that's ruined by way to many ads that pop up freely on their own when you're just changing a tab in game. I wouldn't be so hard on it if it were just to watch the ads when you want to and get double payout or some type of reward.", 'Love it This game keeps me going and is very relaxing. But, when you get higher in the game, you have to watch an ad whenever you click on Mars. I like the app, but not the ads.', "I've always loved these games. They're my favorite evolution games. The only reason I'm not giving it 5 stars is because I ran into a bug that affected my gameplay. I contacted Tapps, but they have not responded. I hope no one runs into this bug too...", 'it literally shows you an ap every half minute. this is ridiculous', "Fabulous game, very addicting, adorable dogs and I'm definitely going to get into trouble for playing it too much when I'm not supposed to >:)", 'I redownloaded this game after over a decade just for the nostalgia. I will tell you now that this game did not disappoint. I still love this game, it is so cute and easy', 'I have played these games on and off for years and i love them! Funny, weird, cute and casual gaming, from getting far in the other evolution games i know it gets even weirder so i cant wait to see all the doggos. Very easy to learn.', 'Amazing! Its such an entertaining game and there are so many different types of dogs! There is a reasonable amount of ads and there is also lots of ways to make the process faster. I totally recommend it, it is a fun and simple game.', 'It\'s a good way to kill time, but I hate the new "evolution boxes" takes you out of gameplay and if I\'m just trying to tap, I cant do that anymore :(', "TO ALL THE PEOPLE WHO GAVE THIS A ONE STAR FOR THE ADS: There is a very free and simple trick to avoid these. TURN OFF YOUR WIFI. Ads can't get through without wifi to transfer it to your screen, so next time you think about complaining about the ads, remember: TURN OFF YOUR GOD DAMN WIFI", "Interesting time waster, but there are so many ads it ruins it. I can't even find the option to purchase the game just to turn off the excessive ads.", "This game is cool but... It has a LOT of ads. Its like they don't care adout there people who play their games. But it fun so if you don't care about ads play this game.", 'So fun! Lots of cute things to do and the doggos are great. All the little details in all of these games are great! (I have 5 from the same company thing)', "Ok think it's a good game but you need to make the poops cost more ,the diamonds easier to get and the cost of power ups cost less.", 'I have bad wifi so idk why ppl are complaining about the freaking adds i only saw 5-6 adds :/ but its simple, and cute, the designs, are, auhh, i like it but the designs, i dont like it.', "Literally everytime I try and open the app it crashesüíî I'm not sure if it's because of my device, but it's really sadüò≠ it's despair induuuuciiiingg- I've played it before though so it is a good game! I pray to Atua it will start workingüëâüëà", "The game is good but there are too many ads so I can't able to play the game properly so fix that issue.", 'Its a really fun and cool app to play. At the super market , the school bus , any where is fun to play', '100000/10 I had been grinding this game for a few years when I had my fire tablet and only had one dog and 2 alien dogs left until my brother smashed the tablet. Very enjoyable tho and I recommend to anyone <3', "You might find the ads annoying but don't worry! You can turn off your WiFi, you can play it offline and online!", "It's very fun and it helps waste time. The graphics are good and its super adorable üòä", "Game is nice, but too many cheap ads just keep popping up like every minute - they're ruining the experience.", "*its just an evolution game about dogs.* *that's it.* Yet it's so creative compared to other evolution games. title: Dog Training App ‚Äî GoDog
description:
POSITIVE-BASED DOG TRAINING. BUILT-IN DOG CLICKER. TRAIN YOUR DOG ANYTIME, ANYWHERE!

Are you a happy dog owner? Do you want to know how to train your dog in easy-to-follow steps? Download GoDog ‚Äî smart guide for dog training and taking good care of your pet.

Here you will find a full lesson‚Äôs pack with step-by-step video instructions verified by professional dog trainers, built-in dog whistle and clicker, health and care diary, time walking schedule, useful articles, and other features that help your dog stay healthy and happy!

DOG TRAINER APP
These are easy-to-grasp and reproduce lessons for your dog that assist you with essential behavioral training. Teach your puppy to be socialized and well-adjusted without overpaying for dog trainer‚Äôs services. All lessons are made together with highly qualified dog trainers. 

You will find different lesson packages, such as Basic (sit, down, stay, no, paw), Good Pup Behavior (come, stop barking, chewing, don‚Äôt jump), Puppy Training Course (potty, collar, come on leash), Dog Tricks and Games, etc. We offer basic lessons for free.

HEALTH DIARY FOR KEEPING YOUR FURRY FRIEND FIT
With the GoDog Health & Care Diary, you'll never forget to take care of your pet. Create reminders for vaccinations, medications, visits to the vet, and other important events in your dog's life and save a history of these events. Track the hygiene care of your doggy including bathing, teeth brushing, nail clipping, ear cleaning, etc. Define dog schedule and let the GoDog app remind you when the next action is due.

WHISTLE AND CLICKER FOR TRAINING DOGS
Use these features to improve and strengthen the results of your dog training exercises. Dog clicker training is gaining popularity for its ease of use and positive effect. Download GoDog and use our built-in dog clicker with 3 different sounds!

WALKING TRACKER
Keep an eye on how much exercise your dog gets on a daily basis. It will help you adjust your walking routine to your dog‚Äôs specific needs.

DOG HEALTH ARTICLES
It‚Äôs extremely important to read up-to-date and verified information so as not to harm the dog. All information and articles in GoDog are checked by professional canine experts and vets, so you can have a rest, while learning something new about your fluffy friend.

Download the GoDog app now and start dog training and spending quality time with your four-legged friend!

Please feel free to contact us: info@godog.me
Privacy Policy: https://www.godog.me/privacy-policy
