title: Herobreeder: Dog breeding app
description:
Meet the only app you‚Äôll need for your dog breeding business.
Here you can set up reminders, plan & map reproduction cycles, and keep track of your dogs from the day they were born, to the day they meet their new family.
No matter if you are a dog breeding beginner, or a breeder with generational experience, HeroBreeder is here to help you keep track of your dog medical information, lets you present your dogs to potential owners more easily, build your brand within dog breeding community, and find out useful tips regarding breeding certain dog breeds. 
HeroBreeder offers three main features to help offload your daily workload more easily:
PLAN & TRACK YOUR ACTIVITIES
Here you can stay on top of all of the important data regarding your dog's progress. Consider it as your personal calendar in which you can set up reminders, and track every important event in your dog‚Äôs life.


Dog profiles
Think of it as your dog‚Äôs ID. One place where you can store all crucial information about each dog. This allows you to closely monitor their basic characteristics and any fluctuation in weight and height, but also helps you optimize the registration process. 


Medicals
If there‚Äôs an ID, why not have a medical file, right? Just what we were thinking when we developed this feature which allows you to track, plan and note all check-ups, therapies, and other medical activity.


Events
Consider it your dog's digital calendar containing every event you insert. The app will categorise and systematise all of them, and remind you when there‚Äôs a task coming up so you don‚Äôt miss out on any of the vaccine shots or check-ups.

REPRODUCTION
Here you can focus on your passion and leave the organizational part to us. Each activity you insert will be shown as events in your calendar. This way you will be able to track your dog's heating and mating cycles, and progress of all the puppies in your litter, from the day they were born until the day you send them to their new home.


Heating
By using the data you inserted, HeroBreeder will be able to create more accurate predictions regarding the coming reproduction cycle of each dog, which will help you better plan your litters. 


Mating
Lets you keep track of mating cycles, when new puppies are due, the statistics of male and female offspring‚Äôs and general mating success rate. 


Litters
Everything you need to keep track of your dog‚Äôs progress, from day one. One of the main features of HeroBreeder which allows you to not only store medical, health and other developmental data, but also lets you keep track of the weight progress of your puppies. This way you can more accurately determine the amount of food, or dose of therapy the dog is advised to receive.

BUILD YOUR BRAND
We are here to help you eliminate the stressing part from your passion for dog breeding, and focus on your four-legged friends. We will enable you with tools to more carefully test and select potential new homes for your puppies, share your passion for a certain breed, and connect with like-minded individuals who understand that dog breeding is not a business, but rather a vocation and a passion.


Present your pups
Create an album and share it on social media or with other breeders and potential new dog owners. You can use this feature for a single dog, a puppy and a whole litter. This will make it easier for you to present your pups and find them a new home.


Tell your story
This is your space, a place where you can share with everyone what drives you, why you are so passionate about breeding, or your expertise regarding a certain breed. Whether it‚Äôs a decades-long family tradition, or you‚Äôre just on your second litter, use this space to share your story and help underline the importance of responsible dog breeding.


Earn on the side
There is always some investment involved, and this feature allows you to organise, plan and keep track of your finances, whether it‚Äôs investment, or income.

Download the app and become a HeroBreeder NOW!
summary: Organize, track & plan your dog breeding business more efficiently

title: Dog Town: Puppy Pet Shop Games
description:
Start your own Dog Town by breeding and collecting dogs. Experience dogs training where your puppies can learn lots of new commands. Train your dog & puppy, send them to quests and funny adventures. Raise your animals and take care of cute puppies in Dog Town simulator games! Pet your puppy, wash, groom, feed like in real life! Enjoy the cute puppy town with unique pet story & training feature. You can get new dog & puppy cards from pet store for your puppy town & collect them. Discover doggy games and customize the rooms where your dogs live! Design your own interiors with hundreds of decorations that you can find in game virtual store. 
 
In Dog Town you can:
 
‚òÖ Train your dogs and teach them lots of tricks with new training feature!
‚òÖ Breed and Collect new dogs! 
‚òÖ Enjoy gorgeous 3D environment! 
‚òÖ Play with realistic Dogs with lifelike behavior!
‚òÖ Take care of your dogs: brush, wash, train, pet & feed!
‚òÖ Level up your dogs and send them to quests!
‚òÖ Decorate your rooms with hundreds of decorations! 
‚òÖ Collect more than 100 dogs and more with each update!
 
If you always wanted to adopt pets or any animal, play with puppies and dogs & were interested in animal shelter, pet & puppy rescue then this is one of the best virtual games for you. Grow your littlest doggo and have fun grooming them . Each animal has a unique character and behavior, so you will always recognize your "Sleepy" from the "Jumpy"! Also you will see their unique behavior while training your puppy. We've put a tremendous amount of effort to ensure that you would feel attached to your animal dogs just like you would to the real ones.
 
In this dog & animal simulation game you can collect dog breeds like: Basset hound, Staffordshire Bull Terrier, Springer Spaniel, Boston Terrier, Labrador Retriever, Australian Shepherd, German Shepherd, Yorkshire Terrier, Bull Terrier, Great Dane, Schnauzer, Cocker Spaniel, French Bulldog, Pomeranian, Doberman, Siberian Husky, Miniature Pinscher, Beagle, Chihuahua, Corgi, Dachshund and other dog breeds. After training your puppies they will become stronger & will participate in more challenging quests. There is a large emphasis on Dog Collection and management for casual and midcore players. 
 
Download now and start having fun with cute pets!
 
 
Enjoyed Dog Town? Join our community:
https://www.facebook.com/groups/382045606113476
 
Please note! This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. If you are having any problems in the game or have a great idea about it please contact gamesupport@frismos.com
summary: Cute doggy rescue story, pets & animal care game. Dogs shelter hotel simulator.

comments: ["The game has a cute style for its models: a satisfying semi-realistic approach. I was curious to see what the game could offer, however I basically wasn't able to get any further than naming my dog as the game freezes upon nearly any action afterwards.", "This game is an absolutely amazing game that works on and offline! I love this game the dogs are Soo cute and it takes like 3-4 minutes to get four puppies!!! This game does have some things that cost money though like the exclusive pack. But I still suggest that you get this game because it can entertain you for hours if you let it! Wonderful game for road trips or long plane rides! Setting it up doesn't take long. Download it today!!!", "This is a great game, for kids, teens and adults!!! Though this game is fantastic I almost have all the dogs, maybe making a cat version of the game would be super cool!!! Just a suggestion I'm sad I almost have finished the game ):", "Back when i was a kid, i always used to play this game, and it was so much fun! The old classic dog game. It has no annoying ads, but this one? It had alot of ads, for every quest, every oven, every tab there is an ad, and if i watched an ad for a free pack, it wasn't working now! I watched an ad, but i didn't receive the rewards. Look, i know the effects of the pandemic caused alot of downhill to most companies, but please, maybe reduce the amount of ads? It's ok if no,iunderstandwhyyoucouldnt.", "It's a fun game and it has cute dogs but I don't like the random ads that pop up and the fact that after you breed and spin the wheel it still shows all the dogs you already have but other then that it's fun to play.", 'Super cute, so many nice animations for a free game. Not many ads at all. But the game keeps crashing unfortunately.', 'Well this game is really fun but it can get a little boring üí§ but it is interesting there are different types of dogs and u can breed them and u can feed and brush and bath the dogs well I totally recommend this game for u well tgats all üëã.', 'Very fun it confused üòï me at first but just click on the brush treat and sponge üßΩ icon to do it but it is fun to breed and üëÄ see what you get. They look so realistic.', "I love this game the dogs are so cute but when I tried to buy more room to put my dog in the room it took my money but it didn't give me more room at all and it happen twice and sometimes there are pop up ads and it does get bothering after a few time", "I get many of the same ads and that gets very annoying but other then that it's a very fun game in my point of view yall should check it out", 'This game is cute, but it does get a bit irritating sometimes. Like, a helping guide would be useful, explaining the purpose of every single thing in the game. Training of the puppies is also confusing. They will move quite rigidly. The puppies need more movement flexibility. Kindly do something to make the game run like butter because it is the only cutest game of puppies, and I love it.', "It's a lovely game, but the ads are really obstructive and annoying. I dont mind an ad every like, 20 mins or so but I'm literally getting them every 5 minutes and each time I get them the game crashes. Please sort the ads out and it will make the experience much more pleasant. x", "Holy Ads, this game is unplayable! Ads every 30 seconds, it's insane!!", "I love this game its fun and so cute what I'm not happy about though are the constant ads and having to pay 8.99 a week for subscription to drop ads and get perks. It's too expensive for a game on my phone.", "I love this game it online but it's fun because you can decorate furniture And you can collect puppy and feed them. They will grow big and you can pet Them.", "This is an amazing game to let off steam and it is exactly what I needed, but there is one awful problem with this game. I deleted the first time I got it because my phone was clogged up, but then I tried to re-download and it had deleted all of my progress. I was on one of the highest levels which I worked extremely hard to get, and now I have to restart which really puts me off. This game would without doubt be 5-stars if it weren't for this annoying mistake. Please fix this üôèüèª.", "I love this game I got so many dogs and it's kinda hard but the dogs are so cute üòç üíì", "I love this game I play it all the time! But now whenever i start the game it doesn't let me in, it says an error has occurred. But besides that (it won't let me in no matter what I do) it's still a good game, oooo adding a newfoundland and irish wolfhound would be awesome!", "It's unfortunately quite buggy. I think it's a super fun(ny) game and would love to play more. But I can put in a lot of time's work which includes watching a bunch of ads (which makes you money) and when I come back, all of that work will be undone (dogs are unleveled, my tokens are gone, etc). May have to uninstall if it persists.", "This game is awesome but it takes forever to load like when I first got it,it loaded fast but I've had it for 2 week's now and it kinda changed so when you get in it takes forever and then you get into the game and this is why I gave it a 4 star rating I hope this helps.", "Just like fun because it's cute seeing alot of puppies running around", 'This game is fun lol I love dogs, but there is some ads', "I really like this game, but I think there are too much ads and bugs. the part that i think can be improved: 1. There are too many ads, like when you want to move room or when you want to collect food (without doubling it). Maybe it's better if you put ads just to get rewards. ex: for packs or speed up things or respin 2. When i watch ads to get double food, it's become 0 not double 3. I think this game is good for children, but some ads in this game is a bit inappropriate for children. Thanks", "Only played this for another game, but not even twenty minutes in I had it uninstalled. The game itself is pretty good. Great animation, adorable dogs, and it's not glitchy too. However, I can't deal with the amount of pop-ups that take up the entire screen‚Äîall of which you can't exit for ten seconds each. I understand that you might need the ad money, but how about giving us optional ads for boosts/speed ups or something. I'm pretty sure so many others are also annoyed by these endless ads.", "It's a good game, really, but I wish there were more things to train the dogs. I feel like we should be able to train working dogs' service dog tasks and things like that. More things related to the breed of dog instead of all of them being the same.", "Logged into the game just fine but there is no dog and I can't go into the little dog store to get a dog cuz they're all locked I went to every section on everything on the screen that I could and could not figure out where this dog is someone please explain to me if I'm doing anything wrong", 'I breed my dogs but then when i come to complete the breeding it like the breeding never happen but when you try to find the dog . It say it still is in breeding . 6 of my best dogs are supposedly still in breeding but when I hit the nest it just gives me the option to breed again .', 'I really love this app as it is a dog game I thought this was not good but turn out to be great! üíØ The dogs breed is alot! I really like that Totally worth to trying to get Ur dog in the game my dog is a shi Tzu and there is in the game thanks that is totally extra credits for the dog town game recommended', "This is the best game ever. There aren't excessive ads, you can get diamonds easily, you can get gold easily, and the dogs are adorable.", "I absolutely LOVE this game! It's fun, adorable, and it teaches young children how to take care of dogs! I love how there are no ads. 10/10 would recommend.", 'Been playing the game for a while and enjoy it. I like the ample opportunities to earn diamonds and money. This is refreshing in comparison to other games that make it nearly impossible to obtain either without spending real money. Thank you. The game is a little glitchy with the dogs either running in place, jerky movements, moving too fast. You may want to iron these glitches out.', 'This game is great! It is a great app to show parents that you can take care of a dog, or for fun! I love everything about it, however it is slightly buggy .. an add pops up sometimes during the tutorial and it still gives me the tutorial but no option to close the add so I have to do it by guessing where everything is. other than that, Awsome game!', "This is a really bad game I mean u can't even enter it üòû. For the first time before I entered it I thought that it'd be sooo fun but I couldn't even enter it. It's really just a fake gameüòíüòï. Soooo not fun üòï. If there was an option I would give it zero stars üòí. I really wish that I could play this game.", "Love the game, but it's pretty glitchy. Graphics are great, there's always something to do, real money isn't needed to advance, it's a cute and addicting game that all ages can enjoy. I do wish there was more you could do with the dogs though, like an outside yard, go on exciting walks, dog clothes choices, i also wish breeding was a little more genetically accurate as well, and i wish that the dogs were more size-accurate. All in all, it's a 10/10 with room to improve üòÅ", "I love this game. It's pretty, cute, friendly and intuitive. One that even the older can appreciate and help them relax. I just think there could be a way to make it less visualy stressing (with a high number of visual elements on the screen later on, with tons of quests pilled and all that).", 'I like it but I wish they had a Foxe dog in the game thanks for listening', "It's a really fun game and I sure do enjoy playing it. However, there is a few issues I have come across. It has way to many glitches, it freezes a lot and it sure does have to many adds. The glitches that it is having...the dogs when they move all of a sudden it's like ether the dogs or the game are freezing.", "This is my favorite game and I will love this game forever good job on making this game I can't wait for games just like this KEEP UP THE GOOD WORK!!!", "I love everything about this game except for spinning the wheel when you have a love story. I literally spun the wheel 10 times in a row watching an ad between each spin to try to get a different breed and more than half the time hit the same exact breed and color for one I already have. This has been a consistent problem and generally makes the game frustrating and not fun to play. I've considered uninstalling multiple times because of this coding choice and now I'm done unless it's fixed.", 'Nice game but too many ads and too lengthy. Mostly at least 30 seconds. Why watch a static company logo or black screen for 30 seconds? Even when you claim something, ads comes out. I understand the need for ads, however ads should be 10 seconds at most. Too much time wasted on ads cannot really enjoy the game. Will rate again if improved.']

title: Cute dogs
description:
‚ñº‚ñº Game description ‚ñº‚ñº
 The game is very simple to play
When matching dogs of same type. a new dog will appear!
The dog that appeared will run around in the dog park to earn money. 
Collect a lot of cute dogs with the money you earned !

‚ñº‚ñº Dogs to appear ‚ñº‚ñº 
30 types of dogs including Corgi, Shiba, Dachshund, Toy Poodle appear !

title: It's a Dog's Love: Romance you
description:
‚ùèSynopsis‚ùè

You expect your new job at Heaven, a famous pet store in Tokyo, will be pretty straightforward -- until you discover your handsome co-workers are actually half-dogs with the ability to transform at will! Dobe, Shephe, and Bernar entrust their secret to you, and you soon find family in the pack at Heaven‚Ä¶ but not all is peaceful. When a rival pet shop sends thugs to destroy the store, you‚Äôre forced to stand your ground and defend your new home alongside your friends. 

Can you save the shop and find romance along the way? Find out in It‚Äôs a Dog‚Äôs Love!

‚ùèCharacters‚ùè

‚óáThe Withdrawn Doberman - Dobe‚óá
Aloof and alert, Dobe is the owner and leader of the pack at Heaven. Though initially cool and difficult to read, as you grow closer, you learn of a tragic event that continues to gnaw at his mind. Will you be able to resolve his past and help him trust again?

‚óáThe Cocky German Shepherd - Shephe‚óá
Shephe may be a little boastful and self-centered, but he‚Äôs fiercely protective of his loved ones and won't go easy on anyone who attempts to harm them. Despite his impressive fighting ability, he harbors some self-doubt and wants to prove himself to you. Will he be the one that captures your heart?

‚óáThe Innocent St. Bernard - Bernar‚óá
Bernar is the little brother of the pack at Heaven. Inquisitive and puppy-like, he adores humans and always sees the best in others ‚Äî especially you! As you work together, he struggles with his newfound feelings of love. Will you show him what it means to be human?
summary: Experience a heartwarming romance with woman's best friend!

comments: ['I\'ve played a dang good amount of these stories. Majority are hits and still somehow have somewhat different plot setups which is refreshing. I really loved the playfulness of this one and I loved it, up until the climax of the plot (before you pick your partner). That felt rushed to me, for some reason. However, I loved the change in the end where you get to pick your comfort level with the guy you picked. Like if you wanted to go all the way that night or "go slow", you decided. ‚ù§Ô∏è', "It's great, very cute story and easy to follow, I personally enjoyed it but I didn't really like the little mini game to earn points, most of the time it only gives my 2 points and it doesn't go any higher than that, the mini game also tends to get boring, I would suggest to put one or two more mini games to make it more fun, other than that I think this app is great :)", 'I really loved the story and the plot! It was just that it upset me knowing that i was out of tickets to get to the next story. Diamonds are easy to get, comparing to other similar games.I really apprecciate the time and effort that the creators/developers put into this game! I really recommend it if you are looking for a love story!', "The storyline and characters are great!!! The only problem I have is that we cant play minigames in between episodes and when we need to make choices. It's a little annoying having to stop the story to play the minigame but other than that, everything is perfect!", "I literally love this but more choices leading up to different routes would be good too , and if you create a point system about the main character's past choices or w/ other characters would be good. I would recommend that. Mostly just more choices to choose from that aren't charging rubies:) overall great app", "Omg, this game is INTENSE! And so are the boys (mainly Dobe) I really hated the fact that I have to wait 4 hours to get points or play one mini-game 100 times (more or less). Also, I'm kinda disappointed over the fact that you can't design your character besides the name. Overall though, I really enjoyed it.", 'I liked the story. the graphics are good. And i really enjoyed it. The reason i didnt put 5 star is bc 1. It was slightly fast paced with there meeting and such. its all based over a few months the first month passing fast. 2. the most important one is the rubies. BE PREPARED TO EITHER SPEND MONEY OR LOTS OF TIME! I didnt take two stars away be they do give u a trading system to get rubies and tickets for apps and actions. But very pricey and each choice is around 25 rubies. I did trade system.', "Love the different options available. My only problem was the spinning for coins. The option for choosing to watch a video is always no videos available. What an inconvenience! If u don't want ur gamers to watch the video then don't put the choice up...", "I love this game! The only thing is that the rubies are so expensive to get if you run out,and the mini game isn't that good either, for example, if you have 3 green hearts that aren't in a line you should still win some ponts but over that the game is awseome. I highly reccomend it with other Genius inc. Games.", "I've played a lot of apps by this company, and this one is probably my least favorite so far. Totally putting aside art, there was no time to actually bond with the characters. This one was really short compared to others I've played, and while I usually do get attached to characters, these guys felt like buddies or siblings, definitely not partners/potential partners.", 'Its not worth it. Frequent ad popups randomly when navigating menus. You can either pay money for Rubies in order to get the premium scenes, or earn points by watching an ad once every 4 hours, or getting lucky in a slot machine game and watch more ads to triple the point payout. You can then exchange points for rubies. The price for rubies is steep. I tried to dismiss the "buy rubies" menu but accidentally bought some without meaning too. I was charged a $35 dollar overdraft because of it.', 'I am just so in love with this app! Cute, adorable dogs, hot guys with the nicest and unique personalites in one and there are 3 of them! Like I mean I cant think of a better app, for real!! üòçüòç Not to mention the choices they give are resonable, unlike many similer apps and the story line is great too. The app is easy to use and not overly complicated. I was literally blushing the whole time‚ù§‚ù§‚ù§‚ù§ love this app!', "This game is soo fun. I absolutely love it and I'm so addicted to it but I only have two complains. 1: why are gems so expensive üò≠üò≠üò≠ please give us a way to earn them or something. 2: can't you make the ticket wait a little shorter please üôÑüôÑ. But at the end of the day really great game I highly recommend it to anyone, especially people with unlimited data and some money. üòÇüòÇüòÅ", "There are no technical issues, very few grammer mistakes but I can't help but feel the storylines and the love interests have a repitive pattern. It feels like playing the same thing over and over again. You need to explore different personalities for both MC and love interests and you need to come up with unique storylines.", "I love this game and I'm not even done playing through it. The characters are all so handsome and sweet and they never fail to surprise me with new parts of their personality. When Bernar said he loved me, I literally erupted in giggles. When Shephe was about to kiss me, I wished so bad that Dobe hadn't walked in. Honestly, I think the game is amazing, and the only thing that really bothers me is the pay-to-play choices.", 'I so love dogs and this app was so cute, however i hate having to reject any of them, they are all cute and but each romantic choice costs so much and every ruby cost so many points, i will have to play hours before i can purchase enough rubies for a free scene, i got one free love scene with just an ad at the beginning chapter but after that, its pay for it. I might reinstall later but i have another yaoi app of yours that i want to finish, please lower your prices so i can enjoy more games.', 'Its great! I love it and the story. I gave it three stars because of the gems, sometimes you end up saying something a bit rude or weird because you dont have enough gems. also the minigame! please add another one ^^ it gets a bit boring after a while overall, its a nice, sure the gems bother me a bit, but i like it!', "I love this game so much. They are all adorable, but it's stupid when I want to earn points to exchange for diamonds. I downloaded 2 games to download and run and it said it would give me 30 or 40 points and then it said we don't have this on the list anymore! So I have to pay for it instead of exchanging!! I hate it! Other than that it's a good game", 'Good game, super cute, and i love it! But the only thing is, ive been playing it for a while. But recently, it wont let me back in and keeps on saying something went wrong everytime i go on it. If you fix this i think MY expirience for the game would be better. But beside that, its a really good game, almost perfect!', "I love the storyline, and the guys(particularly Shephe XD), but... two stars because of the gems, and how you're restricted on what to say. Sometimes, you can answer kinda rudely, but if you really really like that person, and don't have enough gems, there's just no feel for the story! Please please please make the gems no more! Or at least refill the gems everyday or something. All I want is to enjoy a good story, and you're giving me one: but you're also taking all the fun out of it!", "I really like this game. It's a good story to follow along with. You don't get many gems or tickets but I think it's worth the wait. I definitely recommend it, even my friend likes it", 'I love the story it\'s taken me more than 6 months of watching videos and playing the mini game once a day but I loved this app only reason I\'m uninstalling it is because I finished all routes and endings. Though i wish we could have more ways to earn the dimonds to do the questions that require that. Please make it to where we can use our coins that you can earn i think that would make the game even better! I love the way the game makes you feel like your attcualy making contact and talking to the charictors!! I highly recomend the game!!!! Over all one of my favorte games!', "Adorable and cute!üíï The fact that you have me simping over all 3 of them. My only complaint is you have to use a slot machine to get only 2 and 4 coins, also I can't watch videos to multiply by 3. But I don't really care, it's still awesome and I totally recommend this game! üòä", "I've only started playing this and i'm enjoying it already.They all have unique personalities which i'm fascinated of...my only problem is about the gems,why do they cost that much? and it literally makes you wait 2 hours and so on to refill the story tickets but so much for that,I still love the game and i'm looking forward for more of it.", "I LOVE THIS GAME!! I love the characters,the different choices,and how you can have a romance route with all of them without choosing I'm also playing immortal heart I've became a fan of that game and wanted to download and play more of your games I've also downloaded my mystic dragons I'm a fan of ur company now! Keep up the good work and for those of u reading this, you will not be disappointed only the fact u have to save up rubies and wait 2 hrs for 2 tickets but it's worth it!best game evr", 'The game is outstanding...good visuals,storyline and choices but i gotta admit it was a bit frustrating that the premium choices literally takes up all the diamonds and its hard to get it back....', 'So I love this game the stories are addicting! But the thing is I want there to be another way to get tickets other than buying them because I dont spend money on online games and the thing is, I was only able to watch 3 episodes with the 3 tickets and It makes me very sad that I cant watch more episodes, Please fix it please.', "The storyline was amazing! I really hated wasting my gems tho since it's really hard to get gems in the game when you spend them but overall i really liked the plot of the story and the twist in the end! I hope to see more stories like these in the end! :D", "I am absolutely hooked to your games like this, but i have a suggestion, i noticed all of the characters are so pale skinned, would you be willing to add some color to their features besides their hair? Also I was sure than Cain had something to with it since he was the only one who knew we were out, that route would've slapped. Hes involved. Theres tension. Build up. We bust him. title: Barkio: Dog Monitor & Pet Cam
description: Barkio dog monitoring app turns two devices into a smart pet camera. Watch live video of your puppy or cat. Hear if your dog barks, and interact with your pet remotely. Staying close to your pet has never been easier. Helpful Barkio features for all pet parents: - live HD video to watch your dog, puppy, cat and pet - record video and capture a photo during monitoring - hear if your dog barks, howls, whine - see if your dog is calm (motion detection) - upcycle your older cell phone or tablet and give it a new purpose - unlimited distance between you and your dog with WiFi and cellular data - talk to your puppy and communicate remotely - prerecord commands to calm your dog down - 2-way video so your dog can see you too - activity log to see everything your pup has been up to - multiple platforms - keep an eye on your dog through phone, tablet, or laptop - detect signs of separation anxiety in dogs - all family members can monitor their dog, cat or other pet - no need for pet cameras, treat dispensers, or collars For some functionalities, you need to purchase Barkio Premium (free trial available). HOW BARKIO HELPS MONITOR YOUR PET? üëÄ Watch video of your dog See what your pup is doing in a live HD video feed. Is your dog barking, howling, playing, or destroying your new pair of shoes? When the visibility is bad, Night Light can help with brightening up the room and catch the attention of your pet. üëÇ Hear every bark Barkio transmits the sound, so you'll know if your dog is barking, howling, or whining, and you'll be able to calm your pet down remotely. ü•æ Distance is no longer a limit Barkio works on Wi-Fi and LTE, 3G so you can monitor your pet from anywhere - from work, when running errands or when enjoying a night out. üîî Stay notified in every situation When noise is registered, Barkio app will send you a notification with an audio snippet. You'll be able to tell if your dog or cat is noisy and needs your attention. üîã Power-saving background mode When using Barkio security dog monitoring app in the background, the pet monitor will inform you about your dog through notifications. This mode helps to save a lot of battery on your device when monitoring. üó£ Interact with your dog With Barkio pet camera, you can communicate with your puppy remotely, calm it down, or stop your dog from disobeying. Whenever you can't talk to your pet live, you can prerecord your custom voice messages (commands) and use them to ease your dog's anxiety. ‚è∞ Activity log Barkio records noises, videos, or photos from each monitoring.These activity logs help you to understand your dog's behavior, and show any signs of separation anxiety, such as excessive barking, howling, or whining. Share the Activity log with friend or a vet to discuss your dog‚Äôs behavior. üé• Upcycling your older phone or tablet Reuse your older device as the Dog Station and give it a new meaning. No need to purchase expensive hardware cameras, CCTV and IP cameras, or collars when you can recycle and upcycle devices you already have. üêæ Perfect for pets Barkio pet monitor is helpful for dogs cats, and other pets such as parrots, bunnies, hamsters, etc. Barkio can help you with solitude training when your dog shows signs of separation anxiety, and help your fostered pet to feel good in its new home. üì± Monitoring from multiple devices Monitor your dog with multiple devices. Use them as Dog or Person Stations to perfectly fit your needs. üë®‚Äçüë©‚Äçüëß‚Äçüë¶ Synchronized Barkio account All family members can join Barkio and monitor the dog together. üì± Monitor across all platforms Enjoy Barkio dog camera app across all platforms with an easy setup and no extra cost. Visit https://barkio.com for more information about the pet monitoring app. Terms of Use: https://barkio.com/terms
summary: Turn two devices into a video pet monitor and watch over your dog, puppy or cat.

comments: ["This is about the 5th or 6th time that I'm giving this app a try and using a premium account to monitor my pet while I'm on vacation. EACH time I've used it the same problem occurres -  The app works perfectly for 2-3 days, then suddenly stops connecting to the camera. I am extremely disappointed with the app, I will be looking for other alternatives, which is a shame since when the app did work it worked extremely well, but it has proven to be unreliable time and time again.", "I got access to the premium version after doing a pretend review and am updating it now after using it. Functions really well, and really helpful for my dog with seperation anxiety. Only suggestion I would make is it would be great to see a snippet of video with the noise activity log! As is I can't figure out what she is barking at. For this reason I won't pay the premium price for ongoing use as I really need that feature. But if you want real time video then it works great", "Since signing up with the premium app earlier this week I have experienced nothing but problems, it keeps disconnecting and the camera doesn't work. When I was just using the free version I had alot more success with this App. Kinda frustrated and disappointed that I spend the money on this", "It's okay. I think there are better apps. I wish I could set what frequencies it picks up. It constantly tells me my dog is being noisy when it's just the jingle of his collar. Lowering the sensitivity then doesn't pick up his barking. Which makes the notifications just really annoying and constant. The 'just hearing sound' mode is cool but immediately turns off when my screen turns off or I open another app. It needs to stay active, that's the whole point. Might as well stare at the video.", "a little buggy but otherwise good. the audio and motion settings continuously show as 'not set' despite being set. I'm not sure if it exists, or couldn't find it, but there's no option to extend the video in the activity log(?)", "Very good app, it would be nice if the audio commands used the default microphone instead of just the main phone one though, so I could use my earbuds to set commands/talk to my dog. My phone mic doesn't work. Would've contacted support, but there's no support email", "This is a great app, works better than some of the actual pet cams, at a cheaper price and without annoying hardware to set up. My only problem is that the background monitoring is so hidden away. I like to use background monitoring at night while my phone is on charge. But I don't need that during the day at work, notifications are perfect then. So it means I have to trawl through 3 settings screens twice a day. If you put this option in an easy location, it would make this a 5‚≠ê app for me.", "Absolutely wonderful! The app is flawless in my opinion. I had an issue and reached out to them and they not only took care of the problem immediately but gave me 3 months for free. They really care about people and it warms my heart. You don't see that much anymore. Thank you üôè ‚ù§Ô∏è üòä my little furbabies thank you too!!", 'Amazing app to watch my puppy. Night vision with on/off torch feature is a great bonus. The app tells me when my puppy makes a noise or moves around, I like that I can adjust the notifications from low to high sensitivity. Records sounds and images in an activity log which I can then save. No problems with the app so far. Thank you.', 'Seems to work well enough for cats even though many features are designed for dogs. My home station failed less than 1 day into our trip but that may have been a hardware issue.', 'The app is very easy to use, and very effective, carefully designed. Used it to monitor my senior dog while working with his separation anxiety. Can be monitored by 2 devices simultaneously. Very convenient to be able to play prerecorded messages. Very useful the ability to monitor without sound on (i.e. during meetings).', 'App is very convenient to setup and to use , living in a country where upload speed is severly limited , would love to see an option for limited speeds especially when rewatching a recording', "It's decent and works for what it is needed for my mic is super sensitive it seems like at the lowest setting I can pickup myself walking down the stairs and I'm not very loud doing so.so it works!only reason for 4 stats is because it's not just my 1 phone but all phone mics are extremely sensitive and send alot of false notifications.", "Admittedly, I have only tried for a short time so far, but it was easy to set up and seems very easy to use. Just what I needed for a rare occasion when my boy doesn't go with me.", 'I just downloaded this but it seems to be working well on the free trial. My ads were in French and it was hard to figure out how to click out of it because there was no X. Just a question in French and it kept taking me to a website ad when I clicked the wrong word to end the ad.', "Today's update got stuck at installing, had to reinstall. Before this update: Light detection set to auto but have to turn it on and off. Motion detection stops working at times. Have to force stop dog station and restart it for it to work. Happened several times.", "Such a great app! We just moved overseas with our Cane Corso. So he's had a lot of anxiety with the flight and separation anxiety. Doesn't help that we're also in a hotel room where we leave him in a crate. He's used to having free roam of the house. This app is a lifesaver and gives us peace of mind that our dog is not only safe but not too stressed because he can hear our voice. Such a simple setup as well. Using our android phone connected to our IPad left in the room in front of his crate.", "just downloaded the appHoping it's easy to navigate and actually free to monitor without having to pay. UPDATE. SO FAR IT SEEMS TO BE WORKING. I WILL MAKE A FINAL REVIEW ONCE IM AWAY FROM THE HOUSE TRYOMG TO CONNECT. From experience that always seems to be an issue...", "When it works, it's fabulous. Unfortunately a good amount of times I try to use it, it won't show any video, won't play back audio, or disconnects itself entirely.", "It's very convenient and easy to use! I love that I can talk to and see my dogs and I can just use an old phone! I wish it had a better viewing angle like a wideframe or able to scan more of the room but it's not bad! I really enjoy it and have only had it a week or so", 'Very simple to pair your devices and start monitoring right away!! The video is very clear, crisp and clean. Absolutely no regrets and highly recommend anyone to try it!!', 'This app is ok. It suits my purpose, but I do have occasional issues of losing connection to the dog station, which can be frustrating. That could be the other phone though and not the app.', 'I would rate 5 if you didnt have to pay for so many features. The free version m has limited capabilities', "I absolutely love this app because I just got my puppy, and I like to be able to watch him while I'm at work!! I'm giving it 4 stars, though, cause not everyone can afford the premium of all these apps . Oh, and cause it's always telling me that the dog camera isn't connected or that he's resting when really he's playing/moving. But other than that I LOVE iT!!! ü•∞", 'This app is excellent... great way to monitor your pet without having to install cameras.', "just started using this app. seems stabel, and easy to use. I'll update after a couple of weeks.", "This app is great. It has many features and was helpful when I adopted two puppies in February. I loved the trial version enough to subscribe and found the subscription to be very affordable for what you get. However, I needed something with night vision and the old cellphone I was using didn't have that capability so I had to break down and purchase a webcam. Previously I would turn my home lights on remotely, but it was becoming a hassle. Sometimes I just don't have those extra seconds.", 'I have to give this app 4 star. Even though it stopped working on my way to my vacation, the customer service was stellar. They tried really hard to fix the matter and answered my email fast. I understand that bugs can happen and with this system it is almost impossible to trouble shoot until I get back home to the Dog Station. And for the time it worked it was really good. I could see my cats play and listen to any suspicious noises. I strongly recommend!', 'Works well, we use it as a baby monitor! Premium functionality makes a big difference, though. Free version is very limited.', "Great idea, needs more tweaking. Love the ease of this and how you're enabling monitoring without the cost of other expensive equipment. Unfortunately it's a *huge* battery drain on phones (drains mine to low battery within an hour ) and unless you're keep the screen of the app open, it seems to 'check out' and then reconnect, so no way too know if it's monitoring. Please work on battery drain and keeping the app open and on. I'm not sure about the sensivity suitability yet but will feed back.", "Great app, but it's far too pricey for subscription. I can get a camera from Amazon for less than the yearly subscription price.", 'Barkio does exactly what it says on the tin! Very clear in both sound and video! Would definitely be signing up after my free trial!', 'This app is brilliant. Dont know how much it costs as im just using the free trial right now but its perfect, Simple, clear, reliable.', "Awesome app I I recommend if you're exploring your options don't skip this one trust me!", 'Amazing app. It works very well and has interesting features', 'I installed in a hurry, and it was simple and fast. Very nice app', 'This app is great for when you need to watch you pup however if you keep the TV on it will register your dog as being noisy.', "Disconnects from my laptop all the time so I can't even use it when I'm away from home which is the entire reason I got it.", "Love this app. Perfect to keep an eye on my cats when I'm away for the weekend.", 'We are on our first holiday with our Dog, and I remembered a friend recommended this app from a dog trainer. It is fabulous and offers us so much comfort to know our dog is settled when we are out!!']

title: SinglesAroundMe - GPS Dating
description:
At SinglesAroundMe (our nickname is SAM), our focus has always been on building a great local dating app that helps you locate and connect with nearby singles.  Since our initial launch as the world's first location-based GPS dating app in 2010, we have grown our company, evolved the platform and have connected millions of local singles together around the globe, bringing hope, love and opportunity to so many. 

During this period of unprecedented anxiety and social upheaval, we want to help in every way we can. We are concerned not only for the people who we work with, who remain fully-employed, but also about social isolation and the mental health of isolated people globally, as social distancing stretches into the future.¬†

To this end, we have included access to our featured "Destination" search service as part of our basic free membership to allow you to meet people beyond 100 miles (160KM) and all around the world, even if you can't travel there right now. We also are also providing free access to "My Likes‚Äù so you can circle back to people you have "Liked" and would like to connect with. Now you can send them a message or nudge to hopefully match, providing you with a second chance to make a first impression!

Spread the word, build the community and offer one another the gift of human connection at a time when we could all benefit from a hug.

My name is Chris Klotz and I created the SinglesAroundMe dating app for people like you. I met my wife by chance while on the the University of Cambridge ski team in the French Alps and I know that these kinds of chance encounters can lead to great happiness, love and wild romance. I also know there is a bit of luck needed in meeting and dating like-minded singles and I hope that SinglesAroundMe can serendipitously help you to discover and meet someone special that is nearby.

Here are just some of our cool features:

‚òÖ 100% Free to join and discover local singles. Easy registration with Facebook or quickly by form. 

‚òÖ AroundMe: Swipe through profiles of nearby singles and engage with people that interest you.

‚òÖ GPS verified users are displayed as ‚Äúheart pins‚Äù on our patent pending privacy protected  ‚ÄúCheck In Location‚Äù interactive map.

‚òÖ byChance: Meet people you crossed paths with throughout your day.

‚òÖ Mingle Room: Presents the newest and most active members in your area to one another.  

‚òÖ Like" or ‚ÄúDislike" photos and keep a fresh list of all the users you ‚ÄúLike‚Äù.

‚òÖ See who has already ‚ÄúLiked‚Äù your profile. 

‚òÖ Users that match (mutually "Like" each other) can talk for free.

‚òÖ Travelling for work or pleasure beyond your current location? Use the "Destination Search" tool to meet new and interesting people wherever you plan on going. 

‚òÖ Message anyone that interests you and let your personality shine through. 

‚òÖ Keep track of all conversations in the message section.

‚òÖ Check "New Users" that have recently joined in your area.
 
‚òÖ 100% location-based, 100% GPS dating.

‚òÖ Location Privacy: Choose when to "show", "hide" or "shift" your location on the Last Check-In map. 

‚òÖ The last Check-In location gives you the opportunity to verify that the person you're chatting with is really where they say they are and not someone faking it. 

‚òÖ Control how you wish to receive messages by email or app notification or both.

Nudity is strictly prohibited and users can monitor and report any bad behaviour. 

On Valentine's Day, SinglesAroundMe was featured on the cover of the USA Today and on ABC World News Tonight as one of the world's leading dating apps.

From New York to Los Angeles, London to Sydney, Vancouver to Toronto and on college and university campus 's around the world, the SAM app is spreading wildly.

Upgrade to SinglesAroundMe Plus for unlimited daily messaging and to see who has Liked you and so much more. 

Please send us feedback or ask questions directly at customerservice@singlesaroundme.com.

comments: ['So barely started to use, so far , like the options of features and the layout of the UI dashboard and etc. It does have potential, but when I go into the "around me" , it does not load the map fully so I cant see whose around me or not. Just a greyish background , but everything else loads on the screen. So I can\'t fully explore and and see how the "around me" part works, but if you go to the " faces" tab , then you\'ll see a list. Which it\'s not bad, Simple, easy to navigate. To continue.', 'Scam. I feel I have been stolen after having paid for the premium feature. I am looking for friends around the world but the so-called travel feature just won\'t be able to find places such as \'New York\' or \'London\', let alone cities around my State. "No such location". Yeah... The developers might live in a different planet, who knows. No wonder the very few people I did find around me have last logged in around 2012, 2015 at best.', "I just honestly started using it so we will see what happens if anything at all I will rate again in about a month. As of yet I have not had any problems with the app it's easy to use, the layout is simple and it's free. Not hardly any ads which is a very nice feature like a lot of people theses days I'm on limited income so can't afford some of these subscriptions to these sites and so the free ones is where I be going all the time but the ads make me stop using them.", "Had it less than 24 hours and it won't stop bugging me to rate it. Kept it a couple of weeks. Delete Every single person I spoke with on this app was a verifiably fake profile. Many thought they were sneaky by being able to show the profile was in a particular place but then later noticing they were actually in Africa. One person even started to talk to me using their native language. It never did stop bugging me to rate it. Even after I had. The ones that seem real the app required membership.", "This is loaded with bugs for me. I got to the login page once after making an account. Not even an hour and 8% battery loss. Won't load any photos I take. Pics of others don't show including the profile pic. If nothing works in 2 days I'll just uninstall the app. I don't recommend paying for anything on this app. It's been around since 2012 and acts like it's still in hardcore development", "it's a great app oh, it seems like it's free to talk to people. It's a little bit awkward when you find out that there's somebody single right down your block. So people aren't necessarily putting their best picture out there. unfortunately, there are scammers out there and it's hard to tell if somebody really likes you or they're just trying to take advantage of you. yes there are fake females out there.", "It's really tough getting a proper feel for an app when it only opens once every 20 or so tries. Or after you finally uninstall, restart, reinstall, and open the app... Or when you can't navigate properly through the app... Or when you can't see any photos of anyone.", 'ok so who ever manages the app, needs to pay more attention to what profile your putting with the pictures. you have 3 of the 4 likes, all the same profile, but different pictures. you might want to fix this. im not real happy with the overall app or experience. oh and a key point here, that is not shared by the developer is, you have to wink or like someone in order to talk to them.... and ive only had the app, and 2 scammers have hit me up. this is a common thing, but doesnt have to be.', 'The app is great but the check in location messages and who checked you out should be free because it says everything free on the app when you look at it. And where they are from should tell you where they are from like county city and town because sometimes it just says England and not where from in England. It also keeps saying that I carnt register and email address is already in use and registration error It told me to email you apart from those few things it was a really good app thanks Lee', 'I have tried many times to register on this app. Always gives an error "there\'s an error with your gps coordinates". What a waste of time. I use a new phone with Android 9.1 on it and all my other apps work perfectly. What a waste of time', 'Subpar at best you cant really do much with out a subscription. There should be a free trial or some kind of messaging to get the full experience of this app. This app does have great potential but with the limited access make it very difficult to meet people on this app', 'Very poor the app never opens or displays any pictures of people or my profile for that matter cant chat to anyone or basically do anything without paying for it why would anyone pay for something they can even use on the basics. If I could have gave it zero stars I would have i think the idea about it is good but it needs to work first.', "Been checking it out for quite a while now, and it is nothing but bots. Scams. I've been around plenty of apps, and aside from you cant do anything unless you pay a subscription fee, all anyone who messages says is the EXACT same scam message. (There is no way 27 women all say the exact same serious relationship message everytime in the same way) which is too bad. otherwise the app seems to have potential, just expensive and I am especially not paying if all I see is the same scam artistry.", "Only really just started using it. Any reviews other than mine might do better for someone. As I'm already semi invested in one, I don't prefer to spend $20+ per app. I might give this a second review and give it 5 üåü's after a while. For now I'll leave it where it's at 3 seems fitting. I may very well delete, (SAM) is a nice concept with poor/horrible execution. üôä", "Instead of paying money for upgrades, only able to link up with nobody because I am the only person in my nation on it... join a group on Facebook titled : Single Friends,USA. It has 50 state subgroups. It's totally free. The profiles are verified. Post an activity and get singles related conversation there.", 'used to be free to contact other members. now costs money. loaded with fake users. had 2 messages and 4 winks after signing up. they all looked fake. and none were in my area. can no longer message without paying. used to be 100% free. not a lot of users in my area. there are free alternatives with larger user base.', "i downloaded the app just see how it is. disappointed. members around me, well lets just say im years late. All old profiles and not even on line anymore. Even seen a 14 years on here with a profile. like really, wow. you definitely need to relaunch a new version and start over. If you don't wont to go to prison for talking on this app,, then dont download it. underage kids, thats right kids have profiles on here.", "I signed up. The next day can't get on. Keep getting error message. The server sent back something not understood. I tried emailing customer support twice no response. So I am deleting the app. I can't use it.", "Only been on here less than a day and you want a review..OK. so far the only problem I have is that it had my account still open from the last time I had this app so I already had my profile filled out. All of sudden its gone and says I need to have one..tried but it won't let me! Frustating to say the least! Please fix!", 'Registering is easy until you have to enter your location, it never picks up location and only say " error " without location, registration process can not be completed!! No use in sending them an email, they never respond! WON\'T RECOMMEND THIS APP!!!!!', "I find this apt terrible, freezes continuously, won't let you update information such as address or photo.. Or certainly wouldn't me, I uninstalled and reinstalled several times, says I've likes and messages but upon checking.. Nothing.. Glad it's free because I wouldn't pay for this garbage.. Totally unimpressed.", "I can't even load a location making a new account ,I factory reset 2 devices ,uninstalled, reinstalled ,the app just needs to be improved ,or there network needs improvment , buffering of pictures not loading I'm using the latest version of the app and another device now ,and I factory reset both devices so there fresh no doubt ,the app needs work and a lot of fine tuning ,,and a lot of fake profiles,that's just my honest opinion ,,I'm defeated ,I'm a grade 17 ntwk egnr largest telecom usa", "I've delete the app because it wont even open and show one person, the searching location just turns the whole time. Very disappointing. I never even got to see one face and i tried reinstalling it...... same thing happened.", "Im having problems with being able to send messages to respond to conversations. When you click on send it just continues to say load but isn't doing anything. It's like the app has frozen", "I downloaded it with pleasure. I tried to register. But on getting go where I should select country, it did not respond. I clicked register, it says country is required. I tried to select country again it didn't work too. The builder wasted his time in creating an app that cannot be used. And I wasted my megabite in downloading. Why should google play store include an app that's not working properly? Google can improve its store reputation by including only working app", "I love the fact that you can view singles that's literally less than 5 miles away from you you can basically see their whole location face and profile and what they're looking for the only thing that's missing is a live option I wish we could go live on this app that will put the icing on the cake other than that I love the app", "Practically you can't search within any distance even if you try to search locally. NO ONE checks out your profile even if you did not hide it. Since this app gives you no value whatsoever, it does not even make sense to use it as a paid VIP member. App is a total waste of times disallowing you to even edit or delete your profile. This should get a zero star even.", 'Its not uncommon for a dating app to have features locked behind a paywall, yet this one failed almost immediately as soon as I got a message from another user, it required me to subscribe to that paywall. For those who are single and want to save their money, use something other than this app.', 'Cheer üíò anyone tested this app? Why there is such hemorrhoids with a bunch of ads and a lot of bots? üòí App is so-so, as far as I caught, this is just a unmodified copy of the original site likevirt point com, only likevirt has a bunch of real profiles, bonuses for newbies and also there is weight gifts üéÅ. Just for the pleasure register, see the profiles, photos! If you have liked keep liking it! üëçüí™', "Good idea to show who's on the map where you choose by satellite view which I feel me and others would prefer but nobody wants to pay to socialize with people. If this app was free it could see off all the competition literally with the satellite view.", "App is a bit glitchy. It no longer shows photos and every once in a while I have to uninstall and reinstall the app for it to work. Have had some chats on here but haven't met anyone in real life on here yet.", 'NONE of the people who contacted me were even in my state. So if "around me" means the same country, this is a great app. If you want someone within, say, even 100 miles of you, try another app, unless you live in a big city on the east coast in which case you might stand a chance.', "This app looks great, but there isn't enough single Sydney women on it, it shows you all the single and looking for someone girls/guy's, either in your immediate location or right out to global, if more people used this app it would be so cool and so easy to almost instantly organize a date with whatever type of person you feel like on any given occasion, I work hard and haven't got alot time to go out and chase women the old fashion way, so EVERYONE PLEASE GET THIS APP AND START SHARING THE LOVE", 'Every 3 minuted its asking me to rate. Stop!!!! Ill rate after ive actually had a chance to use the damn thing without a pop up popping up to ask me to rate! For crying out loud man. Worse than a 2 year old asking why. I just lowered it again to 1* because even aftere i rated it. Its still asking me to rate it. I literally just paid for the sub. And im about to call and cancel and ask for my money back. Havent even owned it a full day', "I was an early user of this app and though i never met anybody with it i thought it had potential. I cancelled and stopped using this app at least 2 years ago, cut to now. I decide to give the app another try so i install it on my phone and start registration when i finish i'm notified email already in use. Contact cs every day for 4+ days no response nothing, what i really dont get is why my address is in use if i quit 2 years ago. Doesnt sound good to me.", "This app is a scam! Iook at every selfie and u can see there taken professionally by someone else! The model isn't even looking at the phone!I have messaged over 200 woman, some even wanting rose's! And I told them I had extra rose's, and not one reply! So I call it steeling our money!", 'Cheer üíò who checked this dating app? Why there is such a problem with constant advertising? üòì Dating app is so-so, as far as I understood, this is just a unmodified copy of the popular site likevirt point com, only likevirt has a bunch of real profiles, a large selection of partners and also there is weight gifts üíù‚ù§Ô∏è. Just for the pleasure sign in, have funüòçüíã! If you tested keep liking it! üëçüí™', 'I get messages from "women" (could be bots for all I know), but it requires a subscription to reply to them. Hot garbage. If the free product is trash, nobody will use it, and the product will be useless. Don\'t waste your time.', "It would not let me delete my profile. There was no delete profile button. I did not subscribe for that reason. Further, when I went to subscribe screens said pmt by the year 99.00 instead of by month as advertised. Unhonorable, probability of little more than phishing scam + other nefarious intents. Pictures of pretty girls are free & I won't pay to be lied to.", 'I have been approached by more scammers than any other dating app. Reported one to the site admin and that profile is still on there. I have not yet been approached by a legitimate female looking for a relationship. Other than that the site is easy to use and navigate.']

title: PetBacker-Dog Boarding, Sitter
description:
PetBacker connects loving dog walkers, sitters, boarding & groomers with pet owners just like you in all major cities & can help you get a loving trusted Pet sitter who can board your dogs & cats in moments after you make a request. 

PetBacker lets you share and show off your dog & cat photos or hire trusted Pet Sitter for boarding, minding, walking, grooming,spa and daycare. The concept is simple, use PetBacker to get people to take care of your pet when you not available, or earn extra money with your love for animals.

If you own or adopt a pet before & are good in taking care of animals, Petbacker makes it safe and secure for parents and sitters to communicate without revealing phone info until hired. It's safe too with Pet Parents & sitters identities verified. Payment for Sitter is guaranteed as Pet parents pay PetBacker in advance & the payment is released within 7 days at the end of the job.

PetBacker aims to create a community for pet parents, lovers, and petfinder to care for each other pets, which can be kitties, doggie, hamsters, fishes or even reptiles like snake. PetBacker is especially useful when going to airport for a holiday & looking for minders to take care or feed your pets. We work with Veterinarians in some area so that Pet Sitters can contact them during emergency. Download Pet Backer today, don‚Äôt let your cats & dog rover around or become mad paws by caging them, give your cat & dog a vacay too.

For Pet Owner
---- Find Pet Sitter, Dog Walker for Pet Grooming, Boarding or Daycare---
‚Ä¢ If you want pet sitter or home pet hotel nearby, we will match to you instantly. With 1 tap all nearby Pet Sitters & home pet hotels will apply for your job via Text. Skip pet hotels & kennels.

---- Finder for Pet  boarding & walkies ---
‚Ä¢ PetBacker takes your "Request" & sends as woof opportunity to these Pet Sitters, Dog Walkers, groomers who meet your criteria to work on your request & those who are interested to work will reply you, saving time from searching & filtering. Send your dogs for walkies today.

---Compare the Pet Sitter, Dog Walker, Daycare & Pet hotels owner---
‚Ä¢ No longer search through pages of dogs, cats & petfinder classifieds; you will get the best & trusted Pet sitter provider offering the best quotes immediately with private chat. Each application includes an estimated price, previous customer review, ratings & profile.

---Hire the right Pet Sitter & care provider--
‚Ä¢ View ratings & reviews left by peers & get the best, with Dog sitters, Dog minders and Dog walkers being verified with Social & Id. When you're ready, greet, meet & hire the right dogbuddy. No more cattery or dog kennel, give your kitties & doggie the vacay with amenities & facility like indoor accommodations or home garden, even overnight with dog & cat lover in their bed rooms as guests. Make reservation for a pampering spa with treats too. We have connection with vet for veterinary care & vaccinations. Exercise your dog conveniently with our dog walkers & walkzee.

For all Pet Service & Care Providers:
---We source potential pet jobs for you---
Be the cat and dogbuddy when owner going on holiday, get genuine leads anywhere. 
‚Ä¢OnDemand platform: Pet parents who need you can find you immediately with a single tap, even if they don't know about you. Every potential leads will be matched & sent to you directly by petsodia. 
‚Ä¢Sitters Directory: dog & cat parents can find you easily by looking for jobs you have done with your very own page
‚Ä¢Jobs Directory: be proactive, let the dog & cat owners know you can shake a paw or use a dog whistle.

For All Pet Lovers:
--Borrow my doggy and make extra income --
‚Ä¢ If you know why dogs wag or cats meow, able to paw shake, play fetch, use a dog whistle; join us and be rewarded with jobs related to pet boarding, pet minding, doggy daycare, pet sitting, wag walking or signup as our dog backer, dog buddy, doghero to work part time as trustedhousesitter, dog trainer, dog groomer or dog translator!
summary: Get Pet Sitter, Dog walker, Pet Boarding, Taxi & Care. Skip Pet Hotels & Kennels
