comments: ['The app is good in connecting clients to us who provide services. Once a job is offered to a client, pressing the back button on the phone does not allow us to get back to the jobs list, so the app needs to be reset. Sometimes when the app is newly opened, pressing on a job too quickly will not do anything so it needs to be reset. The filter is too restrictive - sometimes just typing the word contact, google, or social can get the account restricted. Overall, useful but can be improved.', "It's always a very difficult task to look for a proper boarding for our little ones. But pet backer makes it very easy and absolutely possible at the tip of the fingers. We loved the reminders and the services . Thank you for helping us to be worry free.", "I've been using the app for many years now and it's been a bit glitchy but I can see they're fixing the issues with time and overall works pretty decent. The services and all the help from the support team is really good.", 'Both the app and the website are extremely confusing, buggy and difficult to use. We found a pet sitter but almost gave up on hiring her because of the horrible user interface.', 'So far my experiences have been good. Most of the pet sitters are very loving and caring. I am thankful that there is an app like petbacker to help us to find reliable pet sitters around. The payment method and security are quite good too.', "1. The app has drop to its lowest point. The system alway wrongly block me as it thinks that I share private information, which is not! How am I supposed to chat on the app? 2. It doesn't make sense that every time I submit boarding request the same people keep approaching to me. So I checked that it's only for the fastest 8 people. It doesn't benefit both parties. 3. The customer services is not helpful and I have a lot of pending tickets, which they never reply and anyhow close them.", "App is great for pet walking services and more as I'm student i do this as a part time work and earn my money. Edit - the app is so much scary I really got every time block by the platform. It's Doesn't allow to converse confidently with the client of mine any wrong word used by me by mistake the dumb AI block me and I loose client", 'Thanks to Petbacker that I am able to find a pet taxi. The apps allow both parties to negotiate the taxi chargers. Once booked, the apps allow you to communicate freely to each other .Thank you, pet backer .', "I used to love this app but it has become a nightmare. You can't say anything without the system thinking it is private information and to unlock your account you need to pay ‚Ç¨650?!?! Communication through the app has become impossible and because of it I can hardly accept bookings anymore. Now I just had an email that they take 25% of my bookings income as I haven't accepted a request in a while. Not even worth taking any bookings then.", "petbacker is good but petbacker there's a lot of bug after update 1. red dot notification is still to notification 2. my latest moments in profile is not appear but if i go to moment i saw my latest moments 3. to withdrawal is 4 days still pending need to contact help center to process my withdrawal. It's not the same as before, just waiting for a while i hope this bug hopefully fix im always message after my job completed üòÖüòÖ thanks petbacker ‚ô•Ô∏è", "The app has become worse over time. Now I dont even get to accept any jobs even when I was notified and immediately went into the app to pick up the job but was told I was too late to respond. Haven't been able to get any job for the longest time, and petbacker should really relook into this matter and make improvements in providing a fair system for everyone. The interface often hangs, and the back button doesn't work and hence have to frequently restart the application.", 'It is always slightly daunting looking for pet boarding,but petbacker make it convenient and a reliable portal to help you ease into looking for the right boarder to suit your needs.... because every owner, every pet and boarder all have different expectations...so I joined petbacker.... because it will match you individual needs ,so they they are very patient with their service....and can help tremendously when you need support, thanks for your help, team @ petbackers', "My Bichon frise Misty has been walking every week solo and with small and big dogs since July. She loves the various parks, mountains, beach and boardwalk with Bianca. I love the photos I get. Misty gets excitable and friendly with everyone. Not Street smart so needs watching. Bianca keeps control with leash as Misty is a chaser and doesn't return to her name. My dog has been loving her twice weekly long walks. I'm very happy with petbackers service. Loads of fun for my dog and helps me too. üòÅ", "My rating as a sitter is 4 however if i were to rate as a client it'd be 5. Overall the app has been really great for providing clients although i don't get that many due to my location (not many wants pet services here in Bangi). The payment is quite hard to get released, I don't want to trouble the clients to review us if they're busy. It also takes a long time for sitters to receive the payment. If the app can make the banking process faster after the owner has reviewed would be great", "Really easy to use. I read the reviews about blocking but I didn't experience this at all. Messages sent and received no problem. This is my first time with Petbacker and will definitely use them again.", 'As a pet sitter it feels as the app is way behind. I was unable to block dates that I was not available to pet sit so I got bookings that I had to decline which is not good for my reputation nor my planning. As a pet owner looking for a dog walker I was satisfied and happy.', 'There is no customer care or email support. They loot both the customer and service providers .....if the service providers quotes 500 they take 25% cut and to the customer they add another 25%. There is no proper response and customer and service providers are at losing end. They do not have proper update on market pricing nor they are willing to correct themselves. Mylopaws is much better when it comes to transportation of pets.', "Horrible. It gets blocked every time I need to use it. Won't show messages or notifications, won't let me edit my request...it's a nightmare", 'This thing with the credits that they deducted for every quote I made "being interested" , without even informing me in advance that there are more than 5 quotes sent to the job poster...what is that. If I knew in advance I wouldn\'t have replied at all. Also the app freezes often and the back button doesn\'t work and I have to close the app and reopen.', 'We were very happy with the care our cats were given for eight weeks. Our cats are generally the nervous type, yet they really enjoyed their time with this caregiver. We would use her again without question.', "The app is good but there are bugs there. For example you can't go back to home screen after you chat with a customer/ pet owner", "Worse than rover. You can't book reoccurring services on a daily basis. It makes you make new requests for each day. If you book services for Mon-Fri, it will show it as 5 days/4 nights. Terrible.", 'YuyangDecember 2019 PetBacker Verified She is so nice!!! My dog spent a good Christmas time with Caroline! I got pics every day, he is so happy every day. Caroline bathed him before we come to pick him, so kind of her! Caroline even bought him some new toys! Oh my god, thank you very much! happy new year!', "Managed to find someone who would cat sit my sick cats for a night easily and they were amazing. Though extending a booking isn't as clear as it should be - it created a new request instead of just simply extending the current booking that we have. Hopefully this gets addressed.", 'Petpacker platform new to me but not my pet sitting job. In the app with some options still a little confusion for pet owner and pet sitter such as dont show the end date of service but instead show the how many times for service instead. Also, customer service are very limited to answering your question when you need it. I still waiting more than 24 hrs now. So far, my service went well. I hope we can track more of customers to use this platform and make it popular in the future.', "So far an excellent experience. Edit The app itself it okay. But it takes way too long to get paid even if you've already completed jobs. I'm now on day 8 after job completion and it's still showing pending.", "This app is getting slow, takes lots of time to load. Please fix this issue. Edited: To the developer, please update this version as it's very hard to contact to the pet parent for their hosting request. This is 2nd review within 2 days. Kindly take some action. Thank you.", 'Been really helpful to meet dogsitters, this is what I have used it for. Reliable and clear.', "Previously our baby was taken care at a regular boarding in Rajajinagar, which was best for her, we assumed. As there bookings were full, we searched and left our baby at Sky Pet Foster. Tanushree was too kind and affectionate towards our baby Pari. It was a pleasure experience for Pari with Tanushree and her baby Sky. We got our Pari's food & walk video updates regularly. It is our baby's second home. Stronly recommended...", 'Convenient way to find pet boarding services according to your preferred location and requirements.', '14days and they still haven\'t paid me. Used to be within 1 week. Now you can\'t even simply speak to the help center anymore because now it\'s a reply upto 24hrs later. Edit -After recieving their reply I can honestly say there is no truth to them needing updated bank details because they only pay through PayPal, which mine hasn\'t changed. When I challenge it all I get is "your payment has been processed please wait 2 to 3 working days" so they can get in contact they are just choosing not to.', "The idea is fantastic but there are some very bothersome issues. I love the idea and generally speaking the app is clear. But there are major issues with notifications. I cannot choose to get additional job alerts or other via email and I NEVER get notifications on the phone. I missed at least 40 jobs because of this! There is no in-app way to get in touch with the management and they have poor response. I would also wish they'd add a calender or the option to sync it with the phone's calender.", 'The idea of the app is great and can help many pet owners. However, numerous issues with using the app forced me to write this review. I only used it 3 times and had to contact customer service 3 times. Two of these times it was about me unable to amend start and end dates of the booking. Then it showed that the booking ended and my sitter could not see withdrawal button. Too cumbersome to use it, all I can say. It sends your request to all backers although you chose the private message option', 'Amazing application to interact with different pets and birds..i have been using it since so long..superb', "Like that the pet sitter can update the route, distance and time take to walk my pet. But it would be better if there's a tab for messages at the bottom with the other request etc instead. Cause i had to press through all the tabs to find the message button and notification button is at the profile page. The inconsistency in those button makes it confusing for first time user.", "Like it's great, but you can't filter on verification type or location properly. I've put in my address half a dozen times and it shows people far too far away for me to feasibly use, even though their reviews are great. If you could just fix those two things that's an instant 5 stars. Let me see who has done a bunch of verifications, and let me see people in my area, and if there are none, the option to expand.", "Extremely helpful but needs work on functionality. As pet parents we don't want to restrict our traveling because of our dogs. It's a challenge to find reliable dog boarding services at short notices and that's where pet backer has done an excellent solution. It helps us connect with all available boarders in a short notice in any area and that's been a boon for me as I have been able to plan out my trips more easily with the dogs, in different cities.", 'The app is not good for the sitters at all. It marks the littelist things as sharing sensitive information and then completely stops you from sending messages unless you buy their ridiculously priced 650 pounds program', 'Great app! Was able to find a sitter for my cat through this app, as people providing sitting/home boaring facilities is quite limited in Mangalore.', 'Was able to get a pet sitter quickly after being cancelled last minute in another service. And the experience was great.']

title: Quiz School | Dog breeds
description: With Quiz School, learn all dog breeds recognized by the Federation Cynologue Internationale (FCI) by playing quizzes. All content in the app is unlockable for free, with the diamonds you earn by playing. The educational content is structured by theme. You can therefore unlock new categories of dog breeds as you progress. For better memorization, Quiz School offers you other game modes: - Review all dog breeds you have already learned - Review your mistakes - Compare your knowledge to other players in a weekly competition Learning is done in a playful way: Quiz School offers different types of questions and different types of progressive and varied quizzes to help you stay motivated! By playing about ten minutes a day, you can manage to master all the content of the application in a few months! Approach üë©‚Äçüéìüë®‚Äçüéì Learning a list of items, like dog breeds, is difficult and boring. Quiz School is a serie of applications designed to make this learning easy, effective and fun: ‚Ä¢ Dog breeds are organized into consistent and progressive content. ‚Ä¢ Learning to identify the dog's name from its photo and then its photo from its name helps you to remember more effectively. ‚Ä¢ The different types of questions help to work on different aspects of memory. ‚Ä¢ Game modes are there to help you review what you've already learned, so you remember what you've learned permanently. ‚Ä¢ Quiz School is a fun app to use. You always learn better if you have fun! Quiz School in detail üîéüê∂ Quiz School offers 4 types of quizzes: ‚Ä¢ Classic quiz: answer all questions with less than 3 errors to get your stars. ‚Ä¢ Timed quiz: answer as many questions as possible in the allotted time to get as many stars as possible. ‚Ä¢ Review quiz: A quiz to review all the breeds of dogs that you have already learned so far in Quiz School. ‚Ä¢ Error correction quiz: Quiz School invites you to review questions for which you made a mistake. Answer correctly to remove all your mistakes! Each quiz consists of a series of questions: ‚Ä¢ ¬´ Guess the dog ¬ª question: You have to guess the dog's name from a photo. ‚Ä¢ ¬´ Guess the photo ¬ª question: You have to find the photo from the dog's name. ‚Ä¢ ¬´ Guess all ¬ª question: Find all the dog breeds of the question. ‚Ä¢ ¬´ Hidden texts ¬ª question: Only the initials are displayed. This is a good exercise to practice remembering the breed of dog on your own. Quizz School offers a multiplayer mode : ‚Ä¢ Answer as many questions as possible in the allotted time ‚Ä¢ Give the best of yourself every week! The application includes more than 60 quizzes structured by themes to teach you dog breeds. The themes are: ‚Ä¢ Common dogs ‚Ä¢ Sheepdogs ‚Ä¢ Retriever, flushing and water dogs ‚Ä¢ Terriers ‚Ä¢ Companion dogs and sighthounds ‚Ä¢ Nordic and primitive dogs ‚Ä¢ Watch dogs ‚Ä¢ Pointing Dogs ‚Ä¢ Scent hounds We are working on adding a multiplayer mode: ‚Ä¢ A common quiz for all players of the same level each week ‚Ä¢ Answer as many questions as possible in the allotted time ‚Ä¢ Give the best of yourself every week!
summary: Dogs and quiz lover? Learn more than 300 dog breeds with hundreds of quizzes!

title: Tamadog - Puppy Pet Dog Games
description:
Have you ever dreamed about having a dog? About a cute little puppy that you will take care of‚Ä¶ Dreams come true with dog life simulator Tamadog. It is your new virtual pet. Care for it, love and make it happy.

Your new virtual friend üê©

Don‚Äôt hesitate and get a dog right now. Such a lovely, charming and cute puppy, who likes having fun, eating yummies and taking selfies. You‚Äôll never get bored with it. Discover the Tamadog‚Äôs bright world with a variety of exciting adventures in dog town.

Meet your new virtual friend in the Tamagotchi dog game. Just look at these cute eyes that will melt your heart‚Ä¶ Play talking puppy games, give it delicious treats, take it for walks and just have fun all day long. Pet dog games are made for love. Give your doggy all your love and it will definitely love you back.  

Check out the Tamadog pet simulator and enjoy taking care of your little faithful friend. Imagine that you are playing dog sim Tamagotchi - now the gameplay is in the real pet world‚Ä¶ It's a dream come true.

TAMADOG COOL FEATURES:

üê∂ VIRTUAL PET IN YOUR REAL HOME. Don't forget to give your pet care everyday. Feed it, clean and play with it. You can play both 3D and AR games mode. Allow the app to use a phone camera and your puppy will appear right inside your house. 
üêï RAISE A SMART PET. Record voice commands and train your dog. From ‚Äúsit down‚Äù to ‚Äúbreak dance‚Äù ‚Äì you can teach your dog lots of cool tricks. Talk to your friend. You doggy is so sociable and eager to learn. That is my dog - you will say proudly. 
üì∏ CAPTURE AMUSING MOMENTS. Take cute selfies with your puppy and its dog life, make hilarious videos and share them with friends.
üé∞ UNLOCK NEW LEVELS. Keep raising a happy pet, play dog games and enjoy extra activities as a reward.
üëó DRESS UP YOUR PUPPY. Stylish suits for agile male pups and fancy dresses for fluffy girl puppies - dress up your little friend trendy.
ü•∞ ULTIMATE CUTENESS. Your new friend loves you and goes head over heels when you rub its belly. Can you imagine that your doggy will gladly lick your nose anytime you move the screen closer? All possible with animal games. 
üéÆ MINI-GAMES. Your puppy is asleep or you just need to relax from the daily routine? Try yourself in exciting mini-games in a dog simulator and set your records. There are a lot of puppy games for free for any taste: shooting bubbles is just as entertaining as healing and grooming your dog in diverse and enjoyable lovely pets mini-games.

The only virtual dog that looks like and feels like a real dog. Feed it, pet it, play with it. Take it wherever you want, your doggy with its pet‚Äôs world is always at hand. You‚Äôll never get bored with it.

Show everyone how adorable your puppy is. Try to catch all the bright moments spending together with your virtual friend in puppy games. Take amusing and funny selfies with your AR dog and create your own photo album full of happy memories.

Your pet is tired? Take a break - play mini puppy games free to not feel bored. Challenge yourself in exciting Match 3 games, while your pet is resting. Discover more than 300 levels of the game and try to finish all them to earn special gifts for your talking dog. Play dog games for free and make your pet happier.

TRY PREMIUM ACCESS 
Subscribe for Premium and get unlimited access to all the AR dog game features:
üçñ Unlock all premium items
üçñ Unlock AR mode
üçñ Free daily coins and diamonds

Time has come! Get a puppy with the Tamadog pet games. Love it, care for it and make sure it is becoming your best friend. üíó
summary: Have fun with cute puppy games and raise your charming dog!

comments: ['This game is ok but at the start if you press dont allow acess to photos you cant go back and change it which is really annoying and it also takes ages to grow up and in the adds it looks like you can like have it on your bed and in real life through your phon but that DOES NOT... work for me but otherwise its a good game.', "My 4 year old managed to some how spend ¬£43 on coins even though I have fingerprint approval I emailed for them to take back all the coins and refund and they refused Not a single coin has been spent, the game hasn't even been played She ended up getting it via an advert", "I understand pay to play games but they make it stupid simple for kids to accidentally buy a $15/WEEK package. Per week. As in $60/mo. That's not an oopsie that's exploitation. They know kids are going to do it and that some parents won't dispute the charges so they're making bank. And the ads are incessant, the game is basically unplayable. My daughter was sitting right next to me and I feel like there were ads every 60 seconds.", "This game is not for three year olds C. T damson mazzthats why you had to pay for it I think you are crazy to think that. anyways I love it so much Yes there are some ads but you mash the X an then your all good üëçso yeah I don't care what people think of it I just know that this is a very fun game and they should be grateful that there even is a game LIKE this. You're welcome people that made this game.", "This app should be taken down. My child downloaded, and I was charged 16.09. I don't even know how the purchase went through. Look at all the other reviews! This is happening way too much! Google really needs to do something about this!", "The game is automatically 5 Star's it took me forever to pick one out of three puppies but when I picked one oh Wow! The game is amazing like your cat game the puppies are adorable so thanks for making these games for us to have as pets", "Wish I could give no stars. My daughter accidentally purchased 40 on this when trying to exit out of the ad to purchase some Mexican thing for the dog. I think it's stupid these games do that with the ads instead of having normal ads where u watch a video etc it has ads for purchasing and if u accidentally hit wrong button it automatically charges u. I have requested a refund from game in Google play & as soon my bank opens tomorrow I'm calling have payment canceled and reversed back as well", "I love it a lot very good app I played a lot that's why I give it five stars it's really amazing ü§© but sometimes there's ads", "I love the game maybe less ads and it's so cool for me cause l just happend to LOVE dogs so keep up the good work people.üëç‚ô•Ô∏èüê∂", "I am loving this game Its so amazing! I hope I can see more animals like baby Cat the color ginger and little baby tiger I know it will be awesome if this game can make one it is going to be my favorite game of all!‚ô° . when I found this game F fell in Love with it: D it was awesome I would say this game is for the people who don't have a dog OR some other type of animal this is a truely lovely game! I will be continue to Play the game and have so muck fun. with it hope you guys get this Letter", "I love this game if you dont want to pay dont pay like it's that simple I love this game it's like you have your own dog just 1 problem too many ads so please fix that and please update it more becuz it just needs more updates but otherwise I love this game and keep up the good work", "Deserves 0 stars. Just refund my money please!!! My 3 year old purchased this silly game by accident and within minutes I requested a cancellation and refund which I was denied. I'm beyond furious, I don't understand how an organization functions like this!!! Very lame game, not even worth the purchase even by choice!", "My son accidentally pressed subscribe and I've been charged three different times Google won't give me a refund and I can't figure out how to end my subscription", 'Just a money grab. WAY too easy to accidentally spend money. My son spent 40$ with just a couple of clicks. Its not even fun. Absolutely Uninstalling this terrible game.', 'The dog is cute but It forces you to Pay a monthly subscription witch is 40$ And the adds TO MANY ADDS!! Also the minigames r soooo boringüòëThere is literally nothing to do. üò°üò°üò°üò°Btw my sister accidentaly payed and got grounded So THANKS ALOT', "Worse app my cousin accidentally pressed the subscription and spent 4k pesos my mom sent me and that was supposed to be spent to my hospital billing I requested a refund within a minute and was denied the next day this is frustrating and ridiculous don't download this app, SCAM!", "Predatory. This is a children's game. As soon as my daughter downloaded and started it, I got a notification that my card was charged. My daughter said she couldn't play until she pressed a button( it was a subscription button). It's very easy to accidentally subscribe. I looked on Google play and saw this app cost 10 dollars a week. 40 dollars a month for a game. Absolutely not.", "I love this app, its so cuuuute. But what I hate about it is that it keep forcing me to pay it and also, there is so many ads. That thing that pops up is so annoying. How am I suppose to enjoy my game when ya'll keep forcing us to payüòí And Oh Gosh! The camera thing scares me. üò± Oh and plus, the game is getting boring. The mini games are so boriiing. I was expecting something fun, but its not. ‚òπ", 'This game is a nice little game for kids it shows responsibility to kids when they get a dogüê∂üê∂üê∂üê∂', "I love it Tama dog is so fun too play I'm about to sleep and I remember tamadog is not sleeping yet", 'I love the game great work big thumbs up!', 'This game collect money from kids without permission or even anything you should uninstall it immediately', 'Really good and the fun and the dogüêï is really cute üòç', 'My daughter loves this game she loves the cute puppy üíïüòç also', "This game is cute you guys are mad and goofy- there's nothing to purchase plus I just want to get the dog into my camera but this game is cute you guys just pay for somethingüòÄ", 'if theres lower than 1 star option, i will select it.. i just had an unauthorized purchased from this app,Nice phising strategy that as soon as the user download the app for free it will give them subscribe or purchase button that they cannot move forward unless they click it. in my case, a minor accidentally click the button then next thing i know, i got an email notification saying thankyou for your purchase. what a smart way of scamming people.', 'You guys are illegally allowing payments through this game, i HAVE parantel lock on my phone, and NO purchases can be done withput my finger print, so please explain exactly how you deducted from my bank account without my permission and without my supposed secure password or fingerprint!!!! Refund my money and stop robbing people. Dont tell me nonsense, youcannot bypass byometric finger print approval.', "Not so bad in mini games and others but one major issue... The ads, shows dog as VR via using camera, what did I end up, game crash after trying it. I'm not gotta play this game when I can't even meet the ads's main advertisement.", 'Steals you money quick. My 5 year old accidently hit yes to the $32 WEEKLY subscription ad that pops up when your in the app. I tried to get a refund. Was denied.', "It was good but you can't play the mini games for long. You always have to exit and start playing the level all over again", "I can't get past the loding stage and then the 2 other times I did get past it it blocked the screen with premium! You have to restart it 10,000 times! And you have to pay for the VR!", "I was charged $130 over the course of ten weeks for a subscription to this game. Here's the thing, I never installed this app nor approved any such purchase. My daughter said she doesn't know anything about this. Furthermore, I had authentication required on my account. Google refuses to refund my money. This is very unfortunate, as this time of year is the toughest for me financially. My work is seasonal. I wish your company would do the right thing and give me a refund.", "I haven't even played this game yet, it's been installing for hours. I think I'll just cancel instead of installing it looks fun, but like most games the advertisements are usually lies and you can tell them right off the back but this one looks pretty legit so that's why I downloaded it but I guess it was a lie too?", 'Very nice thanks to make this game because I am a dog lovers', 'I have the best puppy ever believed or not I do', "My grandson downloaded this, and I can't afford it. How do I cancel this.", "I don't understand a single thing in the add it said that u can do the thing where it animates it in front of you but it's not showing the opinion to do that. Very bad game", "This game is so cute especially for the people who loves dogs.I love this game but you can see that i rated 3-5 stars and it's because there are too many ads and also you're gonna need to pay! Well maybe if you make it free and less ads, a lot of people would probably install it.", 'I love the game as a dog lover this game is awesome I just wanted some free clothing that\'s it anyways it\'s worth your time download it it\'s really cute and fun try it out (btw if 1 star rewiewers sees this there\'s a "Continue with the limited edition") that\'s all great game!', "I downloaded the app and straight away way asked to subscribe to gain extra rewards but no way of playing without it so I decided to uninstall the app if this changes I would be happy to give the app a second chance but until then I'll leave it alone"]

title: Merge Dogs
description:
Merge your dogs, build the ultimate dog racing team and win the race!

Do you have what it takes to be the best dog racer out there? Start by getting small puppies, then upgrade them into bigger faster dogs and earn lots of money!

Features:
- Over 20 different dog breeds to discover including shiba inu, corgi, golden retriever, pug, french bulldog, chihuahua, poodle, beagle, dachshund, dalmatian, dobermann, rottweiler and lots more!
- Idle earnings. Gain coins even while you are away or offline.

Manage your team of super fast dogs. Start your dog racing team now and become a champion!
summary: Build your doggy team and win the race!

comments: ['The design of everything is very simple and cute. The animations and feel of it is very happy. You do have to wait, but the animations help for the wait time since the animation entertains you as you wait. A very fun game overall. Perfect for people who like achievin', "This game was fun at first but it starts playing you when your about the finish the game like not giving you your money and taking your good dogs and replacing them with bad ones ( for example there are 5 pages and I was on the husky on the 4th page and they replaced it with a dog from the fourth page) which may not seem like a big deal but the higher the dog the more epband money so replacing it so you get less and have to wait months for a new dog This game is just impractical don't waste time", "Starts off fun but after you gather a few dog species it becomes very difficult to move in to the next species. especially because the money you gather while the app is off is limited. Fun but has more potential. I've dropped it now.", 'Very addictive. As a dog person this game is perfect for me. If you are a dog person you should download Merge Dogs! The graphics are great. So many new types of dogs to collect. I have used the 2x speed. It is one of the best money makers in the game. The 5 star review has been earned. Download right now!', 'It\'s ok... a bit confusing at first figuring out what to do and what the purpose is of having the dogs run laps in circles... keep thinking they\'re going to get tired and get thirsty... thought it was going to be more like a "real merge three" game, not merge two or more. I do however enjoy "creating" the new dog species! it is original, but it needs improvements overall. gets repetitive and lacks incentive after awhile. but I think many people would like it with a clear explanation of what it is', "Really good game it gets kind of boring because it's just a loop you get a dog you merge the dog then again. I think it's a very good game though.", "I love everything but could get lil boring rarely adds don't have to pay money it's good üòä one thing though there is bugs like sometimes one of the dogs was tiny and hard to see maybe see what's wrong? I recommend the game though ;)", "This game is amazing! There are rarely ads, and the dogs are super cute! The only thing is that it gets boring sometimes but that's okay! PLEASE download this app!!!", "Alright, so, I really enjoyed this game at first. It was super fun, really cute, definitely addictive. However... I'm about halfway through the catalogue both for the grass track and the snow track, and now it's boring. It takes too long to get to the bigger dogs, since you only get two hours of away time. There's an upgrade for two more but... Do I wanna pay to still barely be able to buy two dogs at a higher tier? There just isn't enough to do to keep it fun. Good for a while tho!", "This game started out lots of fun and I was always excited to see all the new dogs you could unlock but as you get into the later stages, sometimes my best dogs are randomly deleted and replaced, I have been playing for a long while so it takes weeks and months to get a new dog but they keep getting replaced before I can get a new dog, it does it often and it's impossible to progress through the game at this point. It takes away from the cute aspects. Example; Lost my Samoyed for a Dalmatian.", 'This is a good mindless game to pass the time, it helped me fall asleep. A tutorial would have been nice, I played for days before I figured it to click on the dogs and rabbits. The look of the pit bull was disappointing. All the dogs are very happy looking except him. The devs had an opportunity to put the beautiful dogs in a positive light and they took a wrong turn with it. Last, I beat both levels in just over a week, more levels would be awesome. I am uninstalling for now.', 'okay. i love the colours and the art style used! they really compliment each other and make the game enjoyable. i REALLY like the ability to buy certain dogs as you level up!! that makes it a lot easier but still challenging enough to keep playing! one thing i would like would be the ability to purchase outfits for certain dogs, with in game watch to earn ads, and ingame cash from the dogs. overall this game is great ‚úåÔ∏è', "Addicting and fun, until the ads stopped working, except, of course, the ads that provide zero benefits, which also happen extremely often now. I tried restarting the app multiple times. No luck. Fix this soon or I will delete. I already had to skip a bunch of rewards that I can't get anymore because I could have gotten them by watching an ad. Not satisfied at all... :( UPDATE: They sort of fixed the issue. I can get a reward from a video once, then I need to restart the app, so 3 from 2 stars.", 'This game is great! So fun! When i downloaded it at first i was a bit skeptical thinking about how hard it would be to get more dogs when i got pretty far in the game but i actually enjoy the way they set it up greatly! How you let the dogs run to collect more coins. Its creative and a good way to not run out as well as you dont have to buy coins or watch ads for them! üòÅ Love the game! Addicting, easy, and loads of fun!', "The game isn't really challenging for the mind. Buy a dog, for ever increasing prices, or wait for a free one. Let it run on the track to make money. Combine two of same to get another dog, of a higher level. That one will get you the same income as the two old dogs, only faster, so merging dogs is usually worth it. The rest (free dogs, 20% discount, double speed) is click bait, you get something and the designers earn money. But in the ent, it's surprisingly funny and addictive. I quite like it.", 'I love this game the only thing I wish they could improve is how long you have to merge the dogs. Anyways the whole rest of the game is great!üòä', 'This game is amazing and I love it. I stayed up late playing this game!! It is awesome!! I recommend it to whoever is looking at this. If you like offline games... This is for you! All you have to do to get rid of the ads is turn off your mobile data (if you have that) or turn off your interet! Then no ads. It does load, but dont worry. This is a 5 star rating!!! Love it so much. Again you can always get rid of the ads by turning off internet or mobile data. Anyway, thats my review! ü•∞üê∂üêïüêï\u200dü¶∫', 'MAGNIFIC DOG MERGE GAME üêï good work. Thank you! üê© I was about to finish the game, so I uninstall it to restart it, so much it is relaxing and awesome . üíï', "This game was fun but you need to add a tutorial for new player's but it does help me fall asleep.", "its a cute game, and the dogs models are adorable. it has a short, simple tutorial which is nice. I just don't like how long it takes to upgrade to the next dog. it's a slow-paced game compared to most idle games but that's not a horrible thing. the in-game purchases are also a bit overpriced. I love it as a time passer, but I'm uninstalling.", "It's a cute game but it just feels so plain and basic. At least in Merge Planes you could get boosters, etc for the track, and there was a leader board. I don't want to watch fifty million ads just to make my dogs go faster, etc. And they don't even go that fast with the ads. Plus, the ads don't always work. You need to do more to this otherwise boring game.", "It's a cute app, but is it fun? sort of, at your lowest stage it's fun and you merge but soon it becomes into a log on, collect reward, buy more dogs, close app, repeat. I do like that the ads aren't forced but I do watch them anyway. 1 video to double my 2 billion? sure why not. most people won't like this but I do like grind fest games. so it's cute and it's grindy, following the popular trend of merge apps. with not anything else thrown in to spice it up, that's about it.", "The cutest game I've played so far. The game is very simple and really good for destressing. Animation is cute, and I get excited every time I get a new dog. I'm unable to play ads though so I can't redeem other features. But overall the game is just really chill and enjoyable.", 'This is a great game. But I have a problem, my progress keeps getting lost! I was at the level were I unlocked the sheltie but I come back the next day and it is gone, i still unlocked it in the book of dogs but did not have it on the track. I probably wont get a reply or a bot reply I just hope that this problem gets fixed.', 'I wanted to like this game, but there are a few things that turned me off. First of which was the farther I got in the game, the speed in which the dogs speed around the track literally made me sick. Visually it was disturbing and maybe should come with a warning. The second thing is why is the pitbull the only vicious looking design. All the other breeds look super sweet and friendly. I think the designers are perpetuating an unfair bias.', 'Fun game, but a while ago(long time) i had much progress on the game when it randomly crashed and wouldnt open, this went on for a week until i gave up. When it finally let me play it deleted most of my progress. It is now crashing again and im thinking it will do what it did previously, nice app, but please fix it so it doesnt delete progress, or atleast let us save it somehow.(im on latest version so that cant be why.)', "This app is so so cute and fun!! But it has a bug that happened to me twice. I don't know how that happened but it was in the snow place that my fastest dog lost two times. So I have to use more money and it's so hard because of slower income because of the bug. And also the away time says I'll get my income for 4 hours when I don't use the app but it's just actually 4 minutes. I was supposed to earn at least a trillion in 4 hours but it just gives me 50 billion. It's a fun game though. = )", 'Stopped playing it last year because constant crashes made it impossible to play. Felt the urge to play it again and glad to see that the crashes have been fixed! Cute and fun way to pass the time!', "Thia game is an adorable idle merge game, there's enough factors that go into each dog that give the game more depth than expected, and I love that it has multiple worlds or zones that play at the same time. The only thing I think the game is lacking is a more solid active playing aspect, I'd like to see some kind of minigame alongside the idle aspects, but it's still a complete game that is worth your time.", "Like the game as a way to kill time. Got to Pom, and it looked like it was floating? Thought nothing of it and continued to play, only to find that when I got a 2nd Pom, they wouldn't merge. Closed the app and restarted - my 2nd Pom is going and the Pom I have has been taken off the track. This has happened twice now.", "I think that the game was very simple and easy. It was very short thought. You barley got any dogs and most other breeds can be left out. I know it is kinda tricky to find nonpopular breeds of dogs, but I still think it's great. To the game creaters, you should make one with cats and the different breeds also. I think the game was very cute and I enjoyed it.", "well.. I liked this game, it was fun to merge the lil doggos to get more doggos. BUT. After getting over half the doggos in the regular one and almost completing the snow one, the game continuously crashes. I open it and not even 2 seconds later it crashes. Not enough time for me to do anything. It's super frustrating because I'm just so close to finishing it. I put a lot of effort into this.", "It's an easy game to pass the time with. But a few too many ads for my liking. It's ok to have ads for bonus things like the 2x speed but i don't like that one automatically plays for 5 seconds when i close the buy-a-dog screen.", 'The music is greatüëç and very happy üòä! I love the dogs üêï ‚ù§ and they are very cute üòç! the racing is adorable ‚ù§!', "great game, I'm enjoying unlocking so many great breeds of dogs. the ads are a bit much but I'm not even mad considering you can use it for speeding up money, leveling up to a higher breed when using money, but it randomly comes up when you arent clicking anything that would start an ad and it gets quite annoy when an ad appears for no reason.", 'after a while you can no longer watch ads because the dogs are going so fast, so every time an ad tried to pop up, you have to watch your dogs run behind a loading screen for about 5-10 seconds.. I miss the "watch an ad to make them go 2x as fast!" or "watch an ad to get the next level of dog!" so yeah, the process is becoming a lot slower but I still love to poke the doggos. its actually quite addicting considering it gets laggy after a while', "Love it! Super cute and fun! However!!! It doesn't do a good job at conveying some things. Things like the X2 multiplier lasts 2 minutes and 30 seconds. And it doesn't tell you how much your max away is. All it tells you is that you'll get 2 more hours of max away if you pay them real cash money. A bit unnecessarily annoying.", 'I love the game so much it is a cute doggy game I love I how you can get different dogs my favorite so far that I have is my best one the dalmation. I love this game! Update) I would like a "Save" feature. I recently uninstalled (For storage and realized "oh fu-".) Reinstalled and lost my progress. If you could add a save feature so i can reload my work would be nice, If its already there then ;-;-', "Got months of playtime out of this. Simple idler with ROCK SOLID design. Art is adorable, control is intuitive, and lots of dogs means it last you a while. A few design elements raise its quality of life as time goes on: The quick-buy button (not real $) for the smallest dog eventually moves up the ladder as you unlock new dogs, so merge chains don't become impossibly long slogs. And you can always tap the dogs on your track for a little extra speed/cash. My new benchmark for merge-style games.", 'A Great Game! So much fun! At first when i downloaded it looked skeptical and confusing thinking about how hard it would be to get more dogs but when i got a bit far in the game, i actually enjoyed the way it was set up. Love the game, Addicting, easy and lots of funs.']

title: Hellopet
description:
‚òÜ‚òÖ‚òÜCute! Fun! Social!‚òÜ‚òÖ‚òÜ

Do you love animals but can‚Äôt adopt your own?

Do you want a friendly companion by your side?

Or do you just love adorable animals?

Then Hellopet‚Äôs for you! Using screen overlay technology, you can have cats, dogs and more cute animals running around your home screen. Or visit My Room to create a fun home for your pets!
Unlock new pets, items, and rooms by collecting or buying cookies! Collect hearts by clearing the I'm Hungry! Mini game! Share your creations in Pet Chat, visit friends‚Äô rooms and leave messages in their Guestbook. Your pet will keep you updated on missed texts, the time, your battery level and much more!

‚ô•ADOPT‚ô•
- When you download Hellopet, choose your first cat or dog for free
- Now you can adopt pets by participating in our newly added Daily Check-in and Pet Chance Event
- Also you can adopt pets by using cookies, purchasing cookies in the Cookie Store, etc.

‚ô•COMMUNITY- PET CHAT‚ô•
- Share funny moments with your pets
- Ask questions about Hellopet to friends
- Pet Chat Gallery mode lets you see the best Pet Chat snaps
- Find new friends
- Share fan art pictures, links, and your favourite Pet Chat posts 

‚ô•The Mini Game - I'm Hungry!‚ô•
- The I‚Äôm Hungry! Game is a challenging puzzle where users feed pets by clearing a level
- Score points for matching 4 or more of the same snack
- Clear levels and receive hearts
- A Wild pet appears on players‚Äô home screen if they clear 5 levels

‚ô•MY ROOM‚ô•
- Decorate My Room with a variety of items that your pets can interact with (wallpaper, flooring, furniture, pet supplies, and more with each update!)
- Feed and use to toys to play with pets
- Take a picture, save, and share your decorated My Room

‚ô•COLLECT HEARTS‚ô•
- Hearts appear above your pets‚Äô heads as you play, feed, and tap your pet
- Get hearts when you decorate My Room, interactive with pets

‚ô•HOMESCREEN‚ô•
- Take pets out from My Room, and they freely run, talk, and play on your screen
- Interact with pets by using Voice Commands and tap ‚Äò!‚Äô speech bubbles when they appear
- Pets‚Äô responses change with your daily mobile habits
- Pets give up to date weather, time, and battery alerts

‚ô•SOCIAL‚ô•
- Send ‚ÄòHello‚Äô messages to Hellopet friends and your pet will briefly visit their home screen
- Send a pet‚Äôs picture with a short message to friends without Hellopet through almost any messenger.

**Join the Hellopet community on Facebook, Twitter and Instagram for events & more**
*FB: https://www.facebook.com/HellopetGlobal
*TW: @hellopet_global
*Insta: @hellopet_global

‚ô•Hellopet Permissions Information‚ô•
Below are the permissions which are necessary in order to operate the Hellopet app. 
Users can use Hellopet without enabling optional permissions.

‚Ä¢Storage(Required): Download update files, saved images, My Room screenshots, and save Pet Chat photos 
‚Ä¢Microphone(Optional): Enables voice commands for your pets
‚Ä¢Contacts(Optional): Enables voice commands to make calls and write SMS messages
‚Ä¢Device ID(Optional): Enables app to recognize ads opened and give rewards

‚ô•Managing permissions‚ô•
Android versions 6.0 and later: Settings> Application Manager> Hellopet> App Permissions> Allow access
Android versions prior to 6.0: Will be required to update to version 6.0 to access the permissions menu

comments: ["Great app! There are a few problems driving me to insanity. The ads are always unavailable, preventing me from earning cookies. When taking the One Minute Quiz, it took longer than expected. I never received my promised cookies from it. I tried purchasing cookies to feed my pet, but it wouldn't allow me to buy the option I had selected. Please fix these problems immediately!", "Great app with cute pets that can run across your screen and do goofy stuff that I love. There's just one issue that I have: I can't find a way to transfer my progress from my old phone to my new phone . I have many pets that I would like to have on my new phone so hopefully it's just something obvious like it often is for me. Hope everyone reading this is having a great day or night!", "I love the game but it could use some updating. I wish there were easier ways to get cookies for the animals and s tuff, but it does work and doesn't glitch out and scam. I also wish there were more varieties of pets and that the pets weren't so expensive, i do appreciate how the animals go off screen when you open another app and enjoy them talking to me.", "August 20, 2023: Event rewards don't work and there is no customer support at all - I've tried. So if you don't mind that, definitely consider this because the pets are cute. I just wouldn't recommend doing any ad rewards or putting any money into it. It's unreliable. The daily check in will earn you cookies to get pets. September 2, 2022: Super cute. I noticed a bug: Tapjoy no longer works.", "Out of all the virtual pet apps I've had, Hellopet has gotta be the best. All of the pets are insanely adorable and unique, they would give daily quotes or facts on my home screen, the pets actually interact with eachother, the I'm Hungry! minigame is pretty interesting, and when I get bored there's also the pet chat I could easily look through. But it's been a while since there even was a new pet which kinda bothers me. Other than that, I 10/10 recommend this app to anyone.", 'I love this game is so cute ü•∞. Also I see some bug in Hellopet, when I completely the tasks to get cookie. It meaning app is error. Today Hellopet was updated new version i looked it new version had fix the bugs/error. I talk smth, when I watched 3 ads to get tickets of pet spin. I see the ads was not showing up it\'s keep to "0/3" ads, I\'m a little bit sad I watched the ads why is keep. Hope you fix the ads keep when get tickets and I rated 4 start ‚ú®‚≠ê. Thanks!', "I love this game. It's really cute also the pets can walk on your home screen and over other apps, which can be annoying but you can turn that feature off. Anyways when I'm bored ill just stroll into pet chat and that entertains me somehow. The only thing about it is that the cookies are really hard to get unless you pay money.", "Hello, I absolutely love HelloPet. The animals are adorable, the app doesn't glitch. There are so many cute decorative options for their room. The only thing I would say is whenever I want the animals to run around on my screen, and it in their room..they never do!! They always run off of my screen and they never come back. How do I get the pets to stay on my screen for more then two seconds?", "I love the game very much but there's just one thing when I'm talking to my friend and in any guest book I have to leave the chat and rejoin to see the message So can you make it an update for when someone's typing it says ‚Ä¶ And then the message will respond Once the person is finished typing and send it Because that will make it really easier But everything else really great", "I was really enjoying this game till it come to the pet commands. The mic won't even recognise the word paw or fortune sit or anything. I will persevere with it for now but I feel if I don't work it out soon I'll end up replacing it with a simular app that works properly. Lots of petentional with this game though seems to of been deserted from developers now or surely there would be a update ü§î", "This is my childhood app. I was around the 7th grade when I installed this, now I'm in college and got a better phone for gaming, installed this again. Really falling in love with my kitty on screen. The only problem is when I already enabled my kitten to run around while apps are running, she disappears in some apps and I wonder why. I hope this gets fixed. I want to see her all the time, I'm having a cat fever. I'm waiting until the day I can get my own cat in real life <33", "Great game! Absolutely love it! I had no problems other than one thing. I went to someone's house/room thing and I saw done sort of custom portrait? Dunno how to get it, and I couldn't find it online. Other wise, it's great!", 'Absolutely adprable! The pets are SO CUTE! A few things i do wish though,is that it were eqsier to earn pets and cookies,able to put as many pets as ypu want on ypur screen,and if they would dissapear when taking screenshots,but come bacl after. All the pwts are so hecking cute,and i love having a small,virtual pet! Ita not too big,and is always on my phone (except when off) adorable, definiy reccomend :3', 'I like the app, but when the pet comes close to the screen, could you make it where the lower part of the animal is not cropped out, because it just looks weird.', "I love this app but it will not let me edit the room where all my animals stay. I try to just use all of the items that I own and have already paid for with cookies, but it tries to tell me that I need kore cookied to use all the items that I already own, not sure why. Besides that, I really do enjoy this app but I would really appreciate if that could be fixed, unless it's supposed to do that?", "This app is so good you see I have always wanted a cat when I was younger and this app inspired me but when I was playing a game from get free cookies I still had 8 of them and each day I went on the app it just kept deleting them.
